\h ROMANOS
\toc1 Paulo Liwakatetigi Romaanotedi
\toc2 Romanos
\toc3 Rm
\mt1 PAULO LIWAKATETIGI ROMAANOTEDI
\ip Paulo didikotibige niЙЎМ¶ica lapo anonakato ЗӨoniotagodi ane liЙЎМ¶eladi nigotaЙЎМ¶a Roma. Roma jaЙЎМ¶aniaaЙЎМ¶ani naЙЎМ¶aca nigotaЙЎМ¶a ane daЙЎМ¶axa me ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶etigi ItГЎlia niЙЎМ¶icoa nokododi. IodaЙЎМ¶awadi romaanotedi odinigaanyetece moiwa moiwitideЙЎМ¶etiogi ijoatawece eletidi iiЙЎМ¶otedi. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi Roma me daЙЎМ¶axa me ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶e, aЙЎМ¶aca liciagi nigotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶icoa nokododi. JiЙЎМ¶idiaa liЙЎМ¶eladi CГ©sar, ninionigi-eliodi romaanotedi, ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane daЙЎМ¶axa me ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi inatawece iiЙЎМ¶o niЙЎМ¶icoa nokododi. CГ©sar diiЙЎМ¶enataka midokoyatigi вҖңЗӨoniotagodi CГ©sarвҖқ. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa meliodi me dakaketema loiigi Cristo, leeЙЎМ¶odi me jakataЙЎМ¶a mida anejinaЙЎМ¶atege loiigi Cristo, leeditibige mejiwaЙЎМ¶ata codaa mejinaЙЎМ¶atalo me ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus, ane iiЙЎМ¶e inoatawece aninoa. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi meliodi anoiatetibece niЙЎМ¶ijo loiigi Cristo.
\ip Paulo iditeloco naЙЎМ¶adi liwakate minatawece oko inoa libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, codaa mee me diЙЎМ¶ica oko ane diЙЎМ¶ica meo anigetiЙЎМ¶ida libeyaceЙЎМ¶egi. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi minatawece oko nigo. Codaa mee me diЙЎМ¶ica oko ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a lodoe AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji leeЙЎМ¶odi meote loenataka ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a. Pida Paulo yalaЙЎМ¶ata niЙЎМ¶ina oko anonakato ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus mepaЙЎМ¶a icota me newiЙЎМ¶atace anigida noko, codaa yalaЙЎМ¶ata AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me daЙЎМ¶adiaa iloikatidi niЙЎМ¶ina oko leeЙЎМ¶odi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco. Eledi yalaЙЎМ¶ata Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me diЙЎМ¶eladetigi niЙЎМ¶ina oko anonakato Jesus, codaa me yaxawa niЙЎМ¶ina oko. NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi Paulo ja yalaЙЎМ¶ata AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji micota maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yajigotediogi lewiЙЎМ¶a judeutedi, codaa eledi yalaЙЎМ¶ata niЙЎМ¶ina oko anonakato ЗӨoniotagodi me leeditibige moyiwaЙЎМ¶adi ane liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco niЙЎМ¶ina oko anida naЙЎМ¶atetigi digoina iiЙЎМ¶o.
\c 1
\s1 Paulo yecoaditibige romaanotedi baanoЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi ЗӨoniotagodi
\p 
\v 1 Ee Paulo. Ee liotagi Jesus Cristo. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eniditediwa me ee liiЙЎМ¶exegi, idiomaЙЎМ¶aditedice me jeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece nibodicetedi anele ane icoЙЎМ¶otedigi miniwataЙЎМ¶a.
\v 2 Jotigide naЙЎМ¶a ligegi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me niwakatee nibodicetedi anele, anoditece niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, analee diniditedini maditaЙЎМ¶a lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 3 NiЙЎМ¶idiwa nibodicetedi anele oditece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Lionigi, ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus Cristo. Odaa mijoa me ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa, ida aneetetege licoЙЎМ¶egi Davi.
\v 4 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yenikamaЙЎМ¶a me ikee me Lionigi Jesus niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a ibake nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi nelegi me yewikatiditace niЙЎМ¶ijo moyeloadi. Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ikee Jesus me diЙЎМ¶ica libeyacaЙЎМ¶ajegi liciagi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me diЙЎМ¶ica libeyacaЙЎМ¶ajegi.
\v 5 Odaa leeЙЎМ¶odi Jesus, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me najigotedoЙЎМ¶owa inoatawece ane ЙЎМ¶odaЙЎМ¶alanaЙЎМ¶a ane daЙЎМ¶a domiЙЎМ¶ica ЙЎМ¶onimaweneЙЎМ¶egi me jakataЙЎМ¶a, codaa eote moko liiЙЎМ¶exedi. Eotedibige me jaxawanaЙЎМ¶a inatawece oko moyiwaЙЎМ¶adi, monakato, codaa modoЙЎМ¶eteta LiboonaЙЎМ¶adi Jesus.
\v 6 Odaa akaami eleditetiwaji awanitege niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eniditedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji makaami nepilidi Jesus Cristo.
\p 
\v 7 Odaa jidi naЙЎМ¶adi notaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi jiwakateetibigaЙЎМ¶aji akaamitawecetiwaji ane ЙЎМ¶adiЙЎМ¶eladi nigotaЙЎМ¶a Roma, ane ЙЎМ¶ademaani AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa eniditedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji makaami loiigi. Jemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЗӨodiodi, codaa me ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus Cristo midioka limedi meletaЙЎМ¶adomi, codaa mowo mele ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali.
\s1 Paulo yotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji codaa diniotagodetalo
\p 
\v 8 Odoejegi nimedi iniotagodetalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji InoenoЙЎМ¶odi leeЙЎМ¶odi akaamitawecetiwaji, leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus Cristo aneotedaЙЎМ¶adomitiwaji. IgaataЙЎМ¶a inatawece niЙЎМ¶ina oko digoina iiЙЎМ¶o odibodiceta ЙЎМ¶atiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egitiwaji.
\v 9 Jibatema AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji manitawece yaaleЙЎМ¶ena niЙЎМ¶ina me jeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece nibodicetedi anele anoditece Lionigi. Odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yowooЙЎМ¶odi mejitece anewi niЙЎМ¶ina meji midioka limedi me idalaЙЎМ¶atibigaЙЎМ¶aji niЙЎМ¶ina me jotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e.
\v 10 Jipokotalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me jakadi me idalitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina natigide, pida nige yemaa.
\v 11 IgaataЙЎМ¶a eliodi me jemaa me ЙЎМ¶adatitiwaji amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a idinaxawanaЙЎМ¶atiwage jibakenaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odixaketedi ane najigotoЙЎМ¶owa Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, me yoniciwaЙЎМ¶adi ЙЎМ¶atiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi.
\v 12 Nige idinaxawanaЙЎМ¶a, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЙЎМ¶adaxawanitetiwaji, codaa me ee, leeЙЎМ¶odi eyiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi, codaa me ЙЎМ¶atiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egitiwaji.
\p 
\v 13 Inioxoadipi, jemaa mowooЙЎМ¶oti melioditibece me yowoogo mejigo idalitaЙЎМ¶awa, pida idioka limedi mida ane idibeyacaЙЎМ¶adi, odaa aЙЎМ¶abotibece mejigo. Pida jemaa me idalitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a jakadi me jaxawa oko anidi makaamitaЙЎМ¶a modiotece Jesus, digo anejigotiogi ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi ane liЙЎМ¶eladi eletidi nigotadi.
\v 14 IgaataЙЎМ¶a jiЙЎМ¶idaa ibakedi ane najigotediwa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me jeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece nibodicetedi anele ane icoЙЎМ¶otedigi miniwataЙЎМ¶a, jeloЙЎМ¶oditiogi greegotedi, inaa ane daЙЎМ¶a greegotedi, oko notaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶aximaЙЎМ¶a aninoa lixaketedi, codaa me niЙЎМ¶ina ane diЙЎМ¶ica lixakedi.
\v 15 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi me jibake minitawece yoniciwaЙЎМ¶a, codaa ja idigo me jeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece nibodicetedi anele ane icoЙЎМ¶otedigi miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji digoida makaamitaЙЎМ¶atiwaji ane ЙЎМ¶adiЙЎМ¶eladi nigotaЙЎМ¶a Roma.
\s1 LoniciwaЙЎМ¶a nibodicetedi anele ane icoЙЎМ¶otedigi miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji
\p 
\v 16 AidiboliЙЎМ¶atece nibodicetedi anele anoditece Cristo ane icoЙЎМ¶otedigi miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, igaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶inoa nibodicetedi anele loniciwaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote lewiЙЎМ¶a inatawece oko anoyiwaЙЎМ¶adi Jesus, odoejedipi judeutedi moyeloЙЎМ¶oditiogi, niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi.
\v 17 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶inoa nibodicetedi anele oikee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote niЙЎМ¶ina oko me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina meniwaЙЎМ¶atakanaЙЎМ¶a, codaa niЙЎМ¶ina me doЙЎМ¶oika meniwaЙЎМ¶atakanaЙЎМ¶a. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eeta AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina oko ane yakadi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji leeЙЎМ¶odi meniwaЙЎМ¶atakanaЙЎМ¶a, joaniЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶ida lewiЙЎМ¶a ane diЙЎМ¶ica liniogo.вҖқ
\s1 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji laagetedipi inatawece oko
\p 
\v 18 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane ideite ditibigimedi ikee lГ©laЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi inoatawece ane libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco oko, leeЙЎМ¶odi me doЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶aditeda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa leeЙЎМ¶odi inoatawece ane beyagi anowote modakapetege eledi oko. LeeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶inoa libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco anowote, odaa aЙЎМ¶oika eledi oko moyowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica anewi anodaaЙЎМ¶eeteda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 19 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko oyakadi moyowooЙЎМ¶odi anodaaЙЎМ¶eeteda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, leeЙЎМ¶odi adinaЙЎМ¶aditini niЙЎМ¶ica anodaaЙЎМ¶eeteda, codaa leeЙЎМ¶odi iniaaЙЎМ¶iniwa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ikeetediogi anodaaЙЎМ¶eeteda.
\v 20 NiЙЎМ¶ijo maleekoka yoeteda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o, niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a jakataЙЎМ¶a me jinataЙЎМ¶a, anodaaЙЎМ¶eeteda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi ane daЙЎМ¶a dinelio, inoatawece dinikee. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko oyakadi moyowooЙЎМ¶odi anodaaЙЎМ¶eeteda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶inoa loenataka. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ina oko aЙЎМ¶oyakadi doЙЎМ¶odi me diЙЎМ¶ica libatiigi.
\v 21 IgaataЙЎМ¶a idaaЙЎМ¶ida moyowooЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, pida aЙЎМ¶odoЙЎМ¶etetalo, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a odiniotagodetalo. Pida niЙЎМ¶inoa lowooko yetoledi, inoa laaleЙЎМ¶enali aЙЎМ¶ica gaantokaaЙЎМ¶ida lixakedi, odaa aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica lowoogo anele.
\v 22 Modi me niwaxinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a, pida yetoledi.
\v 23 AЙЎМ¶alee odoЙЎМ¶etetalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aneliodi nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi, codaa ane daЙЎМ¶a daateda. Odaa joЙЎМ¶odilatitelogo niwicidi latopiwadi oko anepaЙЎМ¶a icota me ma, liwicidi ilaaЙЎМ¶axodi, eijedi, codaa me niЙЎМ¶inoa anodigotinigi iiЙЎМ¶o.
\p 
\v 24 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ika modioteci niЙЎМ¶ica anepaa yemaa laaleЙЎМ¶ena mowo ane beyagi, codaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ika mowo niЙЎМ¶ica anepaaЙЎМ¶oyemaa modigota lolaadi ane ЙЎМ¶oboliЙЎМ¶a.
\v 25 AЙЎМ¶odibatege niЙЎМ¶ica anewi anodaaЙЎМ¶eeteda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, pida odibatege niwitakeco. OdoЙЎМ¶eteta codaa modibatema niЙЎМ¶inoa liidaЙЎМ¶atajedi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, pida baadoЙЎМ¶odoЙЎМ¶etetalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a odibatema. Pida leeditibige midioka limedi me joЙЎМ¶eeЙЎМ¶atalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee. (AmГ©m).
\p 
\v 26 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ikatetece mowote anepaa yemaa laaleЙЎМ¶ena. NiЙЎМ¶ina iwaalepodi jeЙЎМ¶epaaЙЎМ¶opitiwage dinoomatewamigi, ane daЙЎМ¶a lakatigi iwaalo.
\v 27 ЗӨoneleegiwadi idaaЙЎМ¶ee, aЙЎМ¶alee loomatewa iwaalo, odaa jeЙЎМ¶epaaЙЎМ¶opitiwage, owo ane ЙЎМ¶oboliЙЎМ¶a. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi me iloikatidi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji loolatedi niЙЎМ¶ina oko leeЙЎМ¶odi epaaЙЎМ¶owotibige.
\p 
\v 28 NiЙЎМ¶idi oko aЙЎМ¶oyemaa moyowooЙЎМ¶odi anewi anodaaЙЎМ¶eeteda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, joaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ikatetece mowote niЙЎМ¶icoa anepaa lowooko aninokinoa ane beyagi, odaa joЙЎМ¶owote loenataka ane ЙЎМ¶oboliЙЎМ¶a.
\v 29-31 NiЙЎМ¶idi oko nolee inoatawece ane latopaco nibeyaceЙЎМ¶eco; noomatewadi niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a lodawadi, codaa inoatawece nimaweneЙЎМ¶eco mowo ane beyagi, idioka limedi madodigomadadi, codaa idioka limedi mowo ane beyagitema eledi oko. NiЙЎМ¶idi oko daЙЎМ¶axa moceeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, codaa ЙЎМ¶onematagododi, idioka limedi me nidelaЙЎМ¶a, awitakaЙЎМ¶a, inoka oyowo mowo ane beyagitema eledi oko. NiЙЎМ¶idi oko odotaЙЎМ¶atibige eledi, enalaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a oiatiwage eledi oko. NeleЙЎМ¶edi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, aЙЎМ¶odeemitetibige eledi oko moyotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e. AnabakenaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, odiletibige me daaditiЙЎМ¶ica liciagi, lemaanigi monaЙЎМ¶axateloco eledi oko. Idioka limedi modoletibige geladi nimaweneЙЎМ¶eco mowo ane beyagi. NiЙЎМ¶idi oko aЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi eliododipi. AЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica doЙЎМ¶oyowo niЙЎМ¶ica ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a. AjakataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a jinakatonaЙЎМ¶a ane lotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko liciagi. OteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a oyemaa litacepodi. AЙЎМ¶oixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedijo eledi oko libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, codaa aЙЎМ¶oiwikode eledi oko.
\v 32 OyowooЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi mee me leeditibige moyeloadi niЙЎМ¶ina oko aneo niЙЎМ¶inoa ane beyagi. Pida idokee mowote niЙЎМ¶inoa ane beyagi, codaa oyaxawa eledi oko mowo ane beyagi.
\c 2
\s1 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji icota me iwi anodaaЙЎМ¶igotediogi oko
\p 
\v 1 Natigide, akaami ЙЎМ¶odokaaЙЎМ¶edi, ane eni eledi oko mepaЙЎМ¶a abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi. NiЙЎМ¶ida makaamitiwaji aЙЎМ¶akati makamaЙЎМ¶a anapitaЙЎМ¶ati ЙЎМ¶adoenataka, aicoЙЎМ¶ota ganigakaami. IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina me ЙЎМ¶adiЙЎМ¶oatita eledi oko, pida awii liciagi niЙЎМ¶inoa anowote, jiЙЎМ¶ikeeni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adiloikatiti leeЙЎМ¶odi ЙЎМ¶abeyaceЙЎМ¶eco.
\v 2 JowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina me iwi anigotediogi codaa niЙЎМ¶ina me iloikatidi oko anowote niЙЎМ¶inoa ane beyagi.
\v 3 NiЙЎМ¶ida makaami ane ЙЎМ¶ademaanigi me ЙЎМ¶adiЙЎМ¶oatita eledi oko anowo, pida akaami eledi awii ane beyagi. Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica ЙЎМ¶animaweneЙЎМ¶egi daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adiwokoni me ЙЎМ¶adiloikatiti AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 4 Akati ina me diЙЎМ¶ica ane jaoЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me daЙЎМ¶axa meletedoЙЎМ¶odomi, odaa anaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odiloikatidi leeЙЎМ¶odi meliodi me yakadi me dinatitedoЙЎМ¶owa. EjinoЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶oti AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meletedaЙЎМ¶adomi, eotedibige madinilaanitece ЙЎМ¶abeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, odaa opilitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\p 
\v 5 Pida dakake ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶ena, odaa aЙЎМ¶emaani daЙЎМ¶a iigi aneni me ЙЎМ¶adewiki. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meneЙЎМ¶egi yelatedaЙЎМ¶adomi nigicota niЙЎМ¶ica noko nige ikee lГ©laЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi nibeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, codaa eote ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a nige ЙЎМ¶adiloikatiti leeЙЎМ¶odi ЙЎМ¶abeyaceЙЎМ¶eco.
\v 6 IgaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yajigote oninitecibeci oko ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a me loojedi ane loenataka.
\v 7 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko anidioka limedi mowo anele, codaa anodoletibige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iweniЙЎМ¶ide, codaa anoyocaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa anodoletibige lewiЙЎМ¶a miniwataЙЎМ¶a, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yajigote lewiЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ini oko ane daЙЎМ¶adiaaЙЎМ¶ica liniogo.
\v 8 Pida niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko ane adodigomadadi, codaa ane doЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi anewi, pida inoka odioteci ane beyagi, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yelatetema codaa me iloikatidi niЙЎМ¶ina oko liciagi.
\v 9 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote lawikodico codaa me ligecaЙЎМ¶aloЙЎМ¶o inatawece niЙЎМ¶ina oko anowo ane beyagi. Odoejegi me nikatedeloco lawikodico judeutedi, nigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi.
\v 10 Pida niЙЎМ¶ina oko anowo anele, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nelecaЙЎМ¶atee, codaa iweniЙЎМ¶ide miniwataЙЎМ¶a, codaa meote mele laaleЙЎМ¶ena. Odoejedipi judeutedi, nigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi.
\v 11 IgaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aЙЎМ¶ica liomaЙЎМ¶atagi noiigi, pida idokigotedoЙЎМ¶owa digawiniteloco oko.
\p 
\v 12 Inatawece niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane doЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶oditeda liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa aninoa libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, joaniЙЎМ¶idiaa naaЙЎМ¶a. (Pida aleeЙЎМ¶odi me doЙЎМ¶oyoteteteda liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco). Inatawece noiigi judeutedi idiwa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji miditaЙЎМ¶a, pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji iloikatidi leeЙЎМ¶odi aЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco.
\v 13 IgaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aiЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶adi oko daЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi me wajipatalo liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco, pida leeditibige niЙЎМ¶ina oko meyiwaЙЎМ¶adi liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ina oko.
\v 14 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ayajigotediogi liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina oko nige diniomaЙЎМ¶aditema ane yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, idaaЙЎМ¶ida me doЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica ane iiЙЎМ¶ete, odaa boЙЎМ¶oikee moyowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a catiwedi laaleЙЎМ¶ena.
\v 15 NiЙЎМ¶ida anee me newiЙЎМ¶a ikee moyowooЙЎМ¶odi catiwedi laaleЙЎМ¶ena liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. IdiaaЙЎМ¶idi odeemitetece ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a catiwedi laaleЙЎМ¶enali, odaa oikee mewi midiwa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji catiwedi laaleЙЎМ¶ena. Idatibece niЙЎМ¶ica anodeemitetece catiwedi laaleЙЎМ¶ena eetibigeloco, codaa idatibece maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a oikee mele anigida loenatagi.
\v 16 JiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee nigicota niЙЎМ¶ica noko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nige niiЙЎМ¶e Jesus Cristo me iwi anigotediogi niЙЎМ¶ina oko leeЙЎМ¶odi lowooko ane dinaЙЎМ¶aditedini, codaa me niЙЎМ¶inoa loenataka ane dinaЙЎМ¶aditedini. JoaniЙЎМ¶inaaЙЎМ¶oditece niЙЎМ¶inoa nibodicetedi anele ane icoЙЎМ¶otedigi miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, ane jeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece.
\s1 Judeutedi idiaa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji
\p 
\v 17 NiЙЎМ¶ida makaami adinabakenitibecetiwaji makaami judeutedi. Anakatoni liiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s, codaa eni makaami nepilidi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 18 JoЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶oti ane yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi ane diniditelogo liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco etiЙЎМ¶adiiЙЎМ¶axinitece moleetibige inokina ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 19 AЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶awienatakanitiwaji makati makaami ligiilaЙЎМ¶adi ЙЎМ¶oladi, codaa aleetibige daЙЎМ¶akaami nilokokena niЙЎМ¶ina ane idei nexocaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 20 NiЙЎМ¶ida makaamitiwaji aleetibige daЙЎМ¶akaami niiЙЎМ¶axinoЙЎМ¶ododi niЙЎМ¶ina ane diЙЎМ¶icata lixakedi, codaa niЙЎМ¶ina anokateciЙЎМ¶ida lixakedi ademiitiogi micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a nigaanigipawaanigi. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a ane diniditelogo liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco idiwa makaamitaЙЎМ¶atiwaji anoikeetaЙЎМ¶awa inoatawece ЙЎМ¶odixaketedi, codaa anewi.
\v 21 Enice akaamitiwaji ane iiЙЎМ¶axini eledi oko, igaamee ina mecoЙЎМ¶otace akamaЙЎМ¶akaami adiniiЙЎМ¶axini? EloЙЎМ¶otitibece deЙЎМ¶eleta me jolicaЙЎМ¶a, pida akamaЙЎМ¶akaami olicetiwaji.
\v 22 Codaa menitiwaji me daЙЎМ¶a yakadi me joЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶atakanaЙЎМ¶a, pida akamaЙЎМ¶akaami aЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶atakanitiwaji. Codaa ЙЎМ¶adeleЙЎМ¶etedi niwicidi noenataka, pida olicetalo niЙЎМ¶inoa laxedi liЙЎМ¶elatedi niwicidi.
\v 23 Adinabakenitibecetiwaji leeЙЎМ¶odi adinanenitece midiwa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco makaamitaЙЎМ¶a. Pida awii eledi oko me daЙЎМ¶adiaa odeemitetigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji leeЙЎМ¶odi akamaЙЎМ¶akaamitiwaji ate iwaЙЎМ¶ati liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 24 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eeta AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi beyagi modotaЙЎМ¶atibige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji leeЙЎМ¶odi ЙЎМ¶adakataЙЎМ¶a, anakaami judeutedi.вҖқ
\p 
\v 25 NiЙЎМ¶ina makagiti ЙЎМ¶adolaadi mikeenitiwaji makaami nepilidi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, niЙЎМ¶ida ida anawiite niЙЎМ¶ina nigoteteni liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina nige doЙЎМ¶otetenitedatiwaji liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, icaaЙЎМ¶ica akagiti ЙЎМ¶adolaadi, aЙЎМ¶ica mawii, codaa ЙЎМ¶adiciagi niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi (ane daЙЎМ¶a nepiliditeda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji).
\v 26 NiЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi nigoyotete liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji idigote micataЙЎМ¶a doЙЎМ¶oyakagidi lolaadi, codaa nepilidi.
\v 27 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi, nigoyotete liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, oikee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ЙЎМ¶adiloikatititetiwaji anakaami judeutedi, anepaЙЎМ¶a domiЙЎМ¶idiwa makaamitaЙЎМ¶a notaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axiidi ane diniditelogo liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa domaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶aditeweЙЎМ¶egi makagiti ЙЎМ¶adolaadi, pida aЙЎМ¶oteteni liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\p 
\v 28 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko nige judeu, pida anebi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji daЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi eliododipi me judeutedi. Codaa niЙЎМ¶ina ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa nigidokida me yakagidi lolaadi, aЙЎМ¶ica aneletema miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 29 Pida beЙЎМ¶ewi me judeu, codaa mewi me nebi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane judeu catiwedi laaleЙЎМ¶ena. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo ikeeta catiwedi laaleЙЎМ¶ena mewi me nebi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. NotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi ane diniditeloco liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aЙЎМ¶ica nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi deЙЎМ¶eo oko me nebi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji iweniЙЎМ¶ide niЙЎМ¶ina oko anewi me judeu, idiЙЎМ¶ida aЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa iweniЙЎМ¶ide.
\c 3
\s1 JakataЙЎМ¶a me jinakatonaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji
\p 
\v 1 Domige daЙЎМ¶axa mele moko judeu, oЙЎМ¶oa domige ina me doЙЎМ¶oko judeu? Domige ica jaoЙЎМ¶o ina judeu me yakagidi lolaadi me ikee me nebi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji?
\v 2 NiЙЎМ¶ina moko judeu eliodi mele. Odoejegi leeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji najigotedoЙЎМ¶owa lotaЙЎМ¶a me jeloЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶atedibece.
\v 3 Pida eliodi judeutedi aЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi lotaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Odaa manigidaa leeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me deЙЎМ¶eote ijo ane ligegi meote?
\v 4 Ayakadi daantiЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi! LeeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ewi, aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a diwitaka. Pida inoatawece ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi baЙЎМ¶a awitakaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eeta lotaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, mee,
\q1 вҖңIniotagodi,
\q1 leeditibige me dinikee makaami ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina motaЙЎМ¶ani,
\q1 codaa icota maЙЎМ¶ekeni niЙЎМ¶ina anodotaЙЎМ¶atibigaЙЎМ¶aji.вҖқ
\p 
\v 5 ЗӨobeyaceЙЎМ¶egi nige ikee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, mige jakataЙЎМ¶a mejinaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me daЙЎМ¶a iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶ateda niЙЎМ¶ina me ЙЎМ¶odiloikatidi leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶obeyaceЙЎМ¶egi? NiЙЎМ¶ina me jao niЙЎМ¶ida igikaneЙЎМ¶egi, inowiiЙЎМ¶otiogi niЙЎМ¶ina oko anida aneetege niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o me notaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 6 Pida ajakadi mideЙЎМ¶ejatigi igegi. IgaataЙЎМ¶a daaditaЙЎМ¶a iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶ateda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa agotaЙЎМ¶a yakadi me iloikatidi oko leeЙЎМ¶odi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco.
\p 
\v 7 Inatecibece oko modi, вҖңIwitakegi nige ikee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji mewi niЙЎМ¶inoa lotaЙЎМ¶a, codaa nige ilecatiditibigimece LiboonaЙЎМ¶adi, enice igaamee ina me idiloikatidi leeЙЎМ¶odi inoa ibeyaceЙЎМ¶eco?вҖқ
\v 8 Inatibece modi, вҖңJaoЙЎМ¶a ane beyagi ijoatokaaЙЎМ¶a jiwidaaЙЎМ¶a anigida anele niЙЎМ¶ina me jaoЙЎМ¶a ane beyagi.вҖқ Eliodi oko modi me niЙЎМ¶idaa ЙЎМ¶odiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi, odaa beyagi modotaЙЎМ¶atibigoЙЎМ¶oji. Pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a nige iloikatidi niЙЎМ¶idi oko anodotaЙЎМ¶atibigoЙЎМ¶oji.
\s1 AЙЎМ¶icoa iniwa ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a
\p 
\v 9 Enice igamodaaЙЎМ¶ee? Ina anoko judeutedi domigica aneletoЙЎМ¶odomi agoda ЙЎМ¶odiciagi ina ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi? Ee meji aЙЎМ¶ica aneletoЙЎМ¶odomi! IgaataЙЎМ¶a ja jikeenaЙЎМ¶a nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a mida loniciwaЙЎМ¶ateloco inatawece oko, judeu, codaa ane daЙЎМ¶a judeu.
\v 10 NiЙЎМ¶ida diniditelogo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a, modi,
\p вҖңAЙЎМ¶icoa iniwa ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a.
\q1 Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica!
\q1 
\v 11 AЙЎМ¶ica ane yowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a,
\q1 oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a odoletibige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\q1 
\v 12 Inatawece oko eyamaЙЎМ¶aticoace,
\q1 odaa aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica jaoЙЎМ¶a.
\q1 Codaa aЙЎМ¶icoa iniwa aneote anele.
\q1 AЙЎМ¶icoa!
\q1 
\v 13 NiЙЎМ¶inoa niolatedi liciagi Г©meЙЎМ¶egi libegi ane domoke (leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶inoa lotaЙЎМ¶a).
\q1 Idioka limedi moninaaletiniwace oko oibake niЙЎМ¶inoa lotaЙЎМ¶a.
\q1 MicataЙЎМ¶a diЙЎМ¶ini lakeedi niweneeno niolatedi.
\q1 
\v 14 NiЙЎМ¶inoa lotaЙЎМ¶a nixoomaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a
\q1 codaa niЙЎМ¶inoa lotaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶onitiadi.
\q1 
\v 15 YediiЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji moyacilotidi
\q1 codaa moyeloadi oko.
\q1 
\v 16 NiЙЎМ¶ina ane diitiwe oyaaЙЎМ¶adi inoatawece,
\q1 codaa mowo eledi oko magecaЙЎМ¶alo.
\q1 
\v 17 AЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica anodaaЙЎМ¶ee me jakataЙЎМ¶a mele ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena.
\q1 
\v 18 Codaa aЙЎМ¶odeemitetibige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.вҖқ
\p 
\v 19 JowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a inoatawece lotaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane iditedini MoisГ©s mida ane ligegitiogi inatawece oko anidiwa miditaЙЎМ¶a me diЙЎМ¶icata ane yakadi me napitaЙЎМ¶adi loenataka, codaa me diЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi mee me diЙЎМ¶ica libeyaceЙЎМ¶egi nige limedi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iwi anodaaЙЎМ¶igotediogi oko.
\v 20 Enice aЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi mee me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a lodoe AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji daЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi me yotete liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. IgaataЙЎМ¶a liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji onikeetoЙЎМ¶owa minoa ЙЎМ¶obeyaceЙЎМ¶eco.
\s1 AnodaaЙЎМ¶eeta AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote lewiЙЎМ¶a oko
\p 
\v 21 Natigide AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja ikee anodaaЙЎМ¶eeta meote niЙЎМ¶ina oko me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji. AleeЙЎМ¶odi moyotete inoatawece liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco, pida leeЙЎМ¶odi eledi ane niiticogi meote me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji. MoisГ©s eledi ikee niЙЎМ¶ida gela ЙЎМ¶onimaweneЙЎМ¶egi me ЙЎМ¶odeЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, baaniЙЎМ¶ijo moikee niЙЎМ¶ijo eledi anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko niЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶oidi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi.
\v 22 NiЙЎМ¶ica gela ЙЎМ¶onimaweneЙЎМ¶egi me ЙЎМ¶odeЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a baЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko monakato Jesus Cristo, odaa ja iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji. Codaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aЙЎМ¶ica idi lemaanigipi.
\v 23 IgaataЙЎМ¶a inatawece oko inoa libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, codaa aЙЎМ¶icoa iniwa ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a liciagi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, ane daЙЎМ¶axa me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, yapidi, codaa aЙЎМ¶ica libatiigi.
\v 24 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote oko me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi ЙЎМ¶odiwikode, codaa idioka limedi meletedoЙЎМ¶odomi, odaa ja najigotedoЙЎМ¶owa niЙЎМ¶ida ane daЙЎМ¶a domiЙЎМ¶ica ЙЎМ¶onimaweneЙЎМ¶egi me inigaanyaЙЎМ¶atece. Jesus Cristo ja yedia loojedi oko me yakadi me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a yeleo leeЙЎМ¶odi ЙЎМ¶obeyaceЙЎМ¶eco.
\v 25 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niiЙЎМ¶e Jesus Cristo me nadooЙЎМ¶odi lawodi me yeleotetema libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco oko. Jesus yeleo eotedibige me daЙЎМ¶alee yelatedoЙЎМ¶odomi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa me daЙЎМ¶adiaa ЙЎМ¶odiloikatidi leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶obeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, nige jinakatonaЙЎМ¶a Jesus. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji dinatitedoЙЎМ¶owa, joaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi me daЙЎМ¶a ikateda oko diЙЎМ¶idioka limedi me nigo leeЙЎМ¶otedi niЙЎМ¶inoa libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, niЙЎМ¶ijo oko ane newiЙЎМ¶a maleediЙЎМ¶icoateda Jesus. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niiЙЎМ¶e Jesus maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yeleotetema libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco niЙЎМ¶idi oko me ikee me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 26 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eotedibige me ikee me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, codaa me yakadi me ikee me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane nakato Jesus.
\p 
\v 27 Migica ane yakadi me dinabaketibece leeЙЎМ¶odi me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a? JowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a me diЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi! Pida igamige leeЙЎМ¶odi me diЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi me dinabaketibece? LeeЙЎМ¶odi aЙЎМ¶ica ini ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi me yotete liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, pida leeЙЎМ¶odi me nakato Jesus, odaa ja iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 28 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa me jinataЙЎМ¶a oko ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi, pida aleeЙЎМ¶odi deЙЎМ¶eyiwaЙЎМ¶adi inoatawece ane liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\p 
\v 29 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji migepoka NoenoЙЎМ¶oditeda judeutedi? AgodaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a NoenoЙЎМ¶odi ina ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi? AjawienatakanaЙЎМ¶a maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a NoenoЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi.
\v 30 Odaa jinataЙЎМ¶a mokiniwatece me ЗӨonoenoЙЎМ¶odi. Eote me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji judeutedi anida eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi, codaa me niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi anaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶ida eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi.
\v 31 Ja jowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a me ЙЎМ¶odeЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi ЙЎМ¶otiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi. Enice, odaa aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica ane jaoЙЎМ¶ate liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji? Okoo, ida ane jaoЙЎМ¶ate! LeeЙЎМ¶odi ЙЎМ¶otiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi eo me jemaanaЙЎМ¶a mejiwaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶a liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\c 4
\s1 AbraГЈo iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi
\p 
\v 1 NiЙЎМ¶ica jotigide icoolatigi ЙЎМ¶onelokodi AbraГЈo, igamigida ica nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi me yakadi me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a lodoe AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji?
\v 2 DaЙЎМ¶a iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a AbraГЈo leeЙЎМ¶otedi loenataka anele, odaa domaЙЎМ¶a yakadi me dinabaketibece. Pida aЙЎМ¶ica anigetiЙЎМ¶ida leeЙЎМ¶odi daЙЎМ¶a dinabaketibece lodoe AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 3 IgaataЙЎМ¶a mee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a, вҖңAbraГЈo nakato AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa leeЙЎМ¶odi eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji jeЙЎМ¶eote me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ
\v 4 NiЙЎМ¶ina ane diba, oyedia. NiЙЎМ¶ina ane dibatege anoЙЎМ¶eedi, pida loojedi niЙЎМ¶ijo libakedi.
\v 5 (NiЙЎМ¶ida moko aЙЎМ¶ica anigetiЙЎМ¶ida ЙЎМ¶odoenatagitema AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aneo me leeditibige me ЙЎМ¶odedia.) NiЙЎМ¶ina oko ane daЙЎМ¶a diba me docaЙЎМ¶atalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, pida nigeyiwaЙЎМ¶adi Jesus, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote niЙЎМ¶ini oko me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi. IgaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yakadi meote me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko aninoa libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco.
\p 
\v 6 Davi idaa yalaЙЎМ¶ata. Mee niЙЎМ¶ina oko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aneote me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, aiЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi deЙЎМ¶epaaЙЎМ¶eo me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a. Codaa Davi yalaЙЎМ¶ata niЙЎМ¶ica oko anida linikegi, mee,
\q1 
\v 7 вҖңNinitibece niЙЎМ¶ina oko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji baanaЙЎМ¶a ixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice
\q1 codaa me napitaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶icoa libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco.
\q1 
\v 8 Ninitibece niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane daЙЎМ¶a nilaЙЎМ¶aditedeloco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶icoa libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco.вҖқ
\p 
\v 9 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji migijoka eote me ninitibigiwaji niЙЎМ¶ijo oko anoyakagidi lolaadi moikee me nepilidi? OЙЎМ¶oa, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji domige aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶eote me ninitibigiwaji ina ane doЙЎМ¶oyakagidi lolaadi? Ja jinataЙЎМ¶a aneyatigi ligegi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a, mee, вҖңAbraГЈo nakato AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa leeЙЎМ¶odi eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji jeЙЎМ¶eote me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ
\v 10 Igamigicatigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji naЙЎМ¶a yakadi AbraГЈo me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a? Migijo maleediЙЎМ¶icatibige daЙЎМ¶a yakagidi AbraГЈo lolaadi, oЙЎМ¶oa, migijo naЙЎМ¶a yakagidi lolaadi? AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yakadi AbraГЈo me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo maleediЙЎМ¶icatibige daЙЎМ¶a yakagidi lolaadi.
\v 11 Odaa niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi AbraГЈo naЙЎМ¶a yakagidi lolaadi leeЙЎМ¶odi me liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ikee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji neЙЎМ¶eote me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi makaaЙЎМ¶eyiwaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aniЙЎМ¶icatibige daЙЎМ¶a yakagidi lolaadi. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi AbraГЈo me micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a eliodi inatawece oko anonakato AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, aneote AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji, idaaЙЎМ¶ida me doЙЎМ¶oyakagidi lolaadi.
\v 12 AbraГЈo eledi micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a eniodi niЙЎМ¶ina oko anoyakagidi lolaadi, pida niЙЎМ¶ina modioteci anodaaЙЎМ¶ee AbraГЈo me nakato AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji maleediЙЎМ¶icatibige daЙЎМ¶a yakagidi lolaadi.
\s1 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane ligegi me yajigotediogi niЙЎМ¶ina ane eniwaЙЎМ¶atakanaЙЎМ¶a
\p 
\v 13 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote ligegite AbraГЈo codaa niЙЎМ¶ica anida aneetege licoЙЎМ¶egi me nebi inatawece iiЙЎМ¶o. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aЙЎМ¶eote niЙЎМ¶ida ligegiteta AbraГЈo daЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi meyiwaЙЎМ¶adi liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco, pida leeЙЎМ¶odi AbraГЈo me nakato AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Odaa joaniЙЎМ¶idaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 14 Nigeote AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ligegitetege niЙЎМ¶ina anodiletibige diЙЎМ¶idokidata moyiwaЙЎМ¶adi liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji, odaa agotiЙЎМ¶ica jaoЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶otiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi. Codaa niЙЎМ¶ica ligegitedoЙЎМ¶ogi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji agotiЙЎМ¶ica niwalГі.
\v 15 IgaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji icota me yelatetema niЙЎМ¶ina anidiwa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco midiwataЙЎМ¶a ane iditedini MoisГ©s, pida aЙЎМ¶oyotete niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina ane diЙЎМ¶icoateda liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco midiwataЙЎМ¶a, aЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi me laagetedipi leeЙЎМ¶odi doЙЎМ¶oyoteteteda niЙЎМ¶idiwa niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco.
\p 
\v 16 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote ligegitediogi niЙЎМ¶ina anonakato me daЙЎМ¶a ixomaЙЎМ¶atice niЙЎМ¶ina AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane ligegi. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote niЙЎМ¶ida ligegi me yajigotediogi noЙЎМ¶eedi inatawece anida aneetege licoЙЎМ¶egi AbraГЈo leeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji idioka limedi meletedoЙЎМ¶odomi. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aЙЎМ¶inoka yajigote noЙЎМ¶eedi niЙЎМ¶ina anoyotete liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s, pida aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yajigote inatawece niЙЎМ¶ina anonakato digo mijotaЙЎМ¶a AbraГЈo me nakato. Odaa AbraГЈo ja ЙЎМ¶odiodi okotawece ane jinakatonaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 17 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a mee, вҖңJao makaami eniodi eliodi noiigi.вҖқ AbraГЈo nakato AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji jeЙЎМ¶eote me ЙЎМ¶odiodi. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji jiЙЎМ¶iniaa aneote Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a me newiЙЎМ¶atace, codaa me yoe inoatawece niЙЎМ¶inoa analee jinataЙЎМ¶a.
\p 
\v 18 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji jeЙЎМ¶eote ligegite AbraГЈo, meeteta, вҖңIcota meliodi oko anida aneetege licoЙЎМ¶egi.вҖқ AbraГЈo eyiwaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ijo ligegi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote me eniodi eliodi noiigi. Odaa AbraГЈo idioka limedi me nibeotege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote niЙЎМ¶ijo ane ligegiteta, idaaЙЎМ¶idata me daЙЎМ¶adiaa nibeotege mica lionigi, leeЙЎМ¶odi ja daЙЎМ¶axa moxiiЙЎМ¶odi.
\v 19 AbraГЈo ejinaЙЎМ¶a ipegiteloco monaniteci taalia nicaaЙЎМ¶ape. Lolaadi aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica loniciwaЙЎМ¶a. NaЙЎМ¶ajo lodawa ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi Sara eledi daЙЎМ¶axa mopake, ja naЙЎМ¶axatelogo nicaaЙЎМ¶ape iwaalo malee dinigaje. NaЙЎМ¶a yowo AbraГЈo naЙЎМ¶a laxokodipi, pida idokee adinelio eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi.
\v 20 Codaa adawienataka micota niЙЎМ¶ijo ane ligegiteta AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Pida idioka limedi me yoniciwadi metiwaЙЎМ¶ataka, codaa doЙЎМ¶etetalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 21 AbraГЈo ayawie AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji mida nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi meote ane ligegiteta.
\v 22 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote AbraГЈo me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, leeЙЎМ¶odi eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi.
\p 
\v 23-24 NiЙЎМ¶ijo nigegi anee, вҖңAneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ NiЙЎМ¶ida ligegi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aЙЎМ¶ijoka yalaЙЎМ¶ateta AbraГЈo, pida oko eledi yalaЙЎМ¶atedoЙЎМ¶owa. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote me ЙЎМ¶odeЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, niЙЎМ¶ina nige jinakatonaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, aneote me yewiЙЎМ¶atace ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus Cristo.
\v 25 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yajigo Jesus me yeleo leeЙЎМ¶odi ЙЎМ¶obeyaceЙЎМ¶eco. NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja yewikatiditace eotedibige me yakadi meote me ЙЎМ¶odeЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a.
\c 5
\s1 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote me ЙЎМ¶odeЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a
\p 
\v 1 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote me ЙЎМ¶odeЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi me jinakatonaЙЎМ¶a. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote mele ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo aneote ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus Cristo.
\v 2 ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus Cristo ja yomoketedoЙЎМ¶odomi ЙЎМ¶oligi miniЙЎМ¶a lodoe AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Odaa natigide idioka limedi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meletedoЙЎМ¶odomi leeЙЎМ¶odi me jinakatonaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa ЙЎМ¶odinitibece leeЙЎМ¶odi me inibeoonaЙЎМ¶atege me ЙЎМ¶odiweniЙЎМ¶ide ЙЎМ¶odawanaЙЎМ¶aditetege Cristo.
\v 3-4 Codaa ЙЎМ¶odinitibece nige jawikodeeЙЎМ¶a, igaataЙЎМ¶a jowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶odawikodico owo me ЙЎМ¶odoniciwadi me jiboЙЎМ¶atege eletidi ЙЎМ¶odawikodico. Igaanige jixomaЙЎМ¶ateenaЙЎМ¶atedijo niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶odawikodico, odaa ja ЙЎМ¶odixomaЙЎМ¶atice AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ЙЎМ¶odici. Odaa jeЙЎМ¶epaanaЙЎМ¶a jatitaЙЎМ¶ati me inibeoonaЙЎМ¶atege lanokegi ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus Cristo.
\v 5 NiЙЎМ¶ida ane inibeoonaЙЎМ¶atege aЙЎМ¶odinaale, igaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЙЎМ¶odemaa. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji najigotedoЙЎМ¶owa Liwigo ane yeloЙЎМ¶odita ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena meliodi me ЙЎМ¶odemaa.
\p 
\v 6 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo maleediЙЎМ¶icata ЙЎМ¶onimaweneЙЎМ¶egi doЙЎМ¶okomaЙЎМ¶a idinewikatitaЙЎМ¶a, odaa Cristo jeЙЎМ¶enagi yeleotedoЙЎМ¶odomi, anoko abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a. ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus Cristo yeleo niЙЎМ¶ijo noko ane nibikota AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me lemeЙЎМ¶egi.
\v 7 AЙЎМ¶ica oko ane yeleotema eledi oko ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a. Pida ejimetiЙЎМ¶ica oko anabo laaleЙЎМ¶ena me yeleotema eledi oko anele.
\v 8 Pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji baЙЎМ¶a ikee meliodi me ЙЎМ¶odemaa niЙЎМ¶ijo Cristo naЙЎМ¶a yeleotedoЙЎМ¶odomi, idaaЙЎМ¶ida moko abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a.
\p 
\v 9 LeeЙЎМ¶odi Cristo me yeleo, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji jeЙЎМ¶eote me ЙЎМ¶odeЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa natigide aЙЎМ¶alee dakaketema Cristo me noЙЎМ¶a ica AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lГ©laЙЎМ¶atetema ЙЎМ¶obeyaceЙЎМ¶eco.
\v 10 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote moko lokaaЙЎМ¶etedi leeЙЎМ¶odi me yeleotedoЙЎМ¶odomi Lionigi niЙЎМ¶ijo maleeЙЎМ¶oko laxakawepodi. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi daЙЎМ¶adiaaЙЎМ¶ica laЙЎМ¶aliigi meote ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi Lionigi naЙЎМ¶a yewiЙЎМ¶atace.
\v 11 Pida aniЙЎМ¶idokida. AaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odinitibece leeЙЎМ¶odi anodaaЙЎМ¶eeteda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. JoЙЎМ¶oko lokaaЙЎМ¶etedipi leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo aneote ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus Cristo.
\s1 JiciaceekenaЙЎМ¶atiwage AdГЈo ijaa Cristo
\p 
\v 12 NiЙЎМ¶ina noiigi digoina iiЙЎМ¶o owo ane beyagi leeЙЎМ¶odi onijoteci ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi AdГЈo. Odaa leeЙЎМ¶odi nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a, jiЙЎМ¶ida nГ©maЙЎМ¶a. Odaa inatawece oko aЙЎМ¶ica ini ane daЙЎМ¶a yeleo leeЙЎМ¶odi inatawece inoa libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco.
\v 13 AniЙЎМ¶icatibige MoisГ©s daЙЎМ¶a iditedini AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco, niЙЎМ¶inoa libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi. Pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a laagetedipi leeЙЎМ¶odi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco niЙЎМ¶ijo oko. IgaataЙЎМ¶a ate niЙЎМ¶icoa me yajigotediogi liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco.
\v 14 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo maleeЙЎМ¶ijo AdГЈo neЙЎМ¶epaaЙЎМ¶icota MoisГ©s, niЙЎМ¶ida ica nГ©maЙЎМ¶a. Inatawece oko nigo, aЙЎМ¶ica ane iwoko, idaaЙЎМ¶ee me diЙЎМ¶icata libeyaceЙЎМ¶egi digo mijotaЙЎМ¶a AdГЈo libeyaceЙЎМ¶egi, leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo me deЙЎМ¶eyiwaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi.
\p AdГЈo liciagi niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЗӨoneleegiwa aneno niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane niwakatee. IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijoa itoataale ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi ane loenatigi icotiogi inatawece oko.
\v 15 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo libeyaceЙЎМ¶egi AdГЈo baadaЙЎМ¶a liciagi niЙЎМ¶ijo liboonigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Odaa eliodi oko nigo leeЙЎМ¶odi onijoteci niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa, ane AdГЈo, ane yotigimade AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji daЙЎМ¶axa meletedoЙЎМ¶odomi, odaa yajigotediogi eliodi oko noЙЎМ¶eedi ane daЙЎМ¶a domiЙЎМ¶ica nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi moyakadi, pida leeЙЎМ¶odi me ЙЎМ¶odiwikode onijoatece ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane Jesus Cristo.
\v 16 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶onoЙЎМ¶eeditalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a jiciaceekenaЙЎМ¶atege niЙЎМ¶ijo anigotoЙЎМ¶owa libeyaceЙЎМ¶egi AdГЈo. IgaataЙЎМ¶a libeyaceЙЎМ¶egi onijoteci ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa eo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me laagetedipi, codaa me iloikatidi eliodi oko leeЙЎМ¶otedi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco. Pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yajigotediogi noЙЎМ¶eedi eliodi oko anowidi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco. ЗӨonoЙЎМ¶eedi ane najigotedoЙЎМ¶owa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ina meote me ЙЎМ¶odeЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 17 Ewi me leeЙЎМ¶odi libeyaceЙЎМ¶egi onijoteci ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa odaa ja diiticogi nГ©maЙЎМ¶a me dibatoЙЎМ¶owa. Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo aneotedoЙЎМ¶odomi Jesus daЙЎМ¶axa meletoЙЎМ¶odomi, aliciagi AdГЈo anaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yoetoЙЎМ¶odomi. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eliodi meletedoЙЎМ¶odomi, codaa eote ЙЎМ¶onoЙЎМ¶eedi niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a domiЙЎМ¶icata ЙЎМ¶onimaweneЙЎМ¶egi me jakataЙЎМ¶a. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa ЙЎМ¶onoЙЎМ¶eedi niЙЎМ¶ina meote me ЙЎМ¶odeЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko anodibatege noЙЎМ¶eedi idiokaanaЙЎМ¶a limedi me newiЙЎМ¶a miniwataЙЎМ¶a, codaa niiЙЎМ¶enatakanaЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi onijoatece ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa Jesus Cristo ane loenatagi.
\p 
\v 18 Ja jinataЙЎМ¶a me leeЙЎМ¶odi onijoteci ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane daЙЎМ¶a yotete liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja laagetedipi codaa icota me iloikatidi inatawece oko. Odaa idaaЙЎМ¶ee, leeЙЎМ¶odi onijoatece ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja yakadi meote inatawece oko me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji, codaa meote me newiЙЎМ¶atace.
\v 19 LeeЙЎМ¶odi onijoteci ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane deЙЎМ¶eyiwaЙЎМ¶adita liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji odaa eo eliodi oko mabeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a. Odaa idaaЙЎМ¶ee, leeЙЎМ¶odi onijoatece ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa aneyiwaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji jeЙЎМ¶eote meliodi oko iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji.
\p 
\v 20 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji iiЙЎМ¶e MoisГ©s me iditedini liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco eotedibige me ikeetediogi oko minoa libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eo oko mepaanaЙЎМ¶a owote libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶axa libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco niЙЎМ¶ina oko, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶axa me ikeete me daЙЎМ¶axa meletetema oko.
\v 21 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco oko mida loniciwaЙЎМ¶ateloco, leeЙЎМ¶odi meo me yeleo. Pida idokee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me daЙЎМ¶axa meletedoЙЎМ¶odomi, odaa jeЙЎМ¶eote me ЙЎМ¶odeЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, ЙЎМ¶odiciagi Cristo, codaa meote ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶a ane daЙЎМ¶adiaaЙЎМ¶ica liniogo MiniwataЙЎМ¶a, leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo ane loenatagitedoЙЎМ¶odomi ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus Cristo.
\c 6
\s1 Gela ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi Cristo
\p 
\v 1 Enice, amiida ica ane daЙЎМ¶axa mele me jaoЙЎМ¶a? Domige midapaЙЎМ¶a jiiЙЎМ¶aticogi me jaoЙЎМ¶a ane beyagi, me jaoЙЎМ¶atibige me ikee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me daЙЎМ¶axa meletedoЙЎМ¶odomi?
\v 2 Ayakadi diЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ejinaЙЎМ¶a! IgaataЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odiciagi niЙЎМ¶ina oko Г©meЙЎМ¶egi ane daЙЎМ¶adiaa yakadi meo ane beyagi. Odaa ayakadi diЙЎМ¶idioka limedi me jaoЙЎМ¶a ane beyagi.
\v 3 Doane mele mowooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji. NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a idinilegenaЙЎМ¶a, jikeenaЙЎМ¶a moko nepilidi Jesus Cristo, odaa micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odemaЙЎМ¶awa.
\v 4 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee, niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a idinilegenaЙЎМ¶a, micataЙЎМ¶a daantaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odeleo, odaa micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odoomatewa noЙЎМ¶onaligitedini Cristo. Eote maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶atace, ja gela anejinaЙЎМ¶a, digo mijoataЙЎМ¶a Cristo naЙЎМ¶a yewiЙЎМ¶atace leeЙЎМ¶odi nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi Eliodi ane jopooЙЎМ¶a.
\p 
\v 5 Nige micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odemaЙЎМ¶awa Cristo, nigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi ЙЎМ¶odewikaЙЎМ¶awa, odaa ja gela anejinaЙЎМ¶a, digo mijoataЙЎМ¶a Cristo me yewiЙЎМ¶atace.
\v 6 IgaataЙЎМ¶a jowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a Cristo me yeleotedoЙЎМ¶odomi madataЙЎМ¶a nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide anejinaЙЎМ¶a, aneo me jaoЙЎМ¶a ane beyagi, ja ma, micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a lemaЙЎМ¶awa Cristo madataЙЎМ¶a nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate, niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a yeleo. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica loniciwaЙЎМ¶atoЙЎМ¶oloco.
\v 7 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko naЙЎМ¶a yeleo, jaЙЎМ¶anipetema loniciwaЙЎМ¶a nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a.
\p 
\v 8 Nige micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odemaЙЎМ¶awa Cristo, odaa ajawienatakanaЙЎМ¶a maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a icota me ЙЎМ¶odewikaЙЎМ¶awa.
\v 9 IgaataЙЎМ¶a jowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a Cristo me yewiЙЎМ¶atace, odaa aЙЎМ¶alee yeleo. LeeЙЎМ¶odi nГ©maЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica loniciwaЙЎМ¶atelogo.
\v 10 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a yeleo, yeleotetema nibeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, odaa onijoteci me yeleo, odaa aЙЎМ¶alee leeditibige daЙЎМ¶a yeleotace. Pida iniwa me yewiЙЎМ¶a me iweniЙЎМ¶ide AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 11 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee akaami eleditetiwaji leeditibige madiniciaceekenitege oko baanaЙЎМ¶a nigo, ane daЙЎМ¶adiaa yakadi mowo ane beyagi. Pida adiniciaceekenitege niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane newiЙЎМ¶a maweniЙЎМ¶idenitetiwaji AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, leeЙЎМ¶odi me ЙЎМ¶adexocitege ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus Cristo.
\p 
\v 12 Odaa jinaЙЎМ¶a domiЙЎМ¶ikani nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a iiЙЎМ¶e ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶ena mawiite niЙЎМ¶inoa ane beyagi ane lidaЙЎМ¶ataka ЙЎМ¶adolaadi anicota me daa.
\v 13 Codaa jiniЙЎМ¶ikanitece ЙЎМ¶adolaadi nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a me ibake meo ane beyagi. Pida adinajicitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji micataЙЎМ¶a oko ane nigo baanaЙЎМ¶a newiЙЎМ¶atace. Ajicitalo inatawece ЙЎМ¶adolaadi me ibake mawii ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 14 NibeyacaЙЎМ¶a ayakadi daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adiiЙЎМ¶eni. LeeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji daЙЎМ¶axa meletedaЙЎМ¶adomi, odaa adibatedaЙЎМ¶agi daЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi me iwaЙЎМ¶ati niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco ane nadeegi MoisГ©s. Pida dibatedaЙЎМ¶agi leeЙЎМ¶odi meliodi meletedaЙЎМ¶adomi.
\s1 Leeditibige me jaoЙЎМ¶a ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a
\p 
\v 15 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji dibatedoЙЎМ¶ogi leeЙЎМ¶odi daЙЎМ¶axa meletedoЙЎМ¶odomi, adibatedoЙЎМ¶ogi daЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi mejiwaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco ane nadeegi MoisГ©s. NigeletedoЙЎМ¶omi, odaa agodiЙЎМ¶ica liaagi ina me jaoЙЎМ¶a ane beyagi?
\v 16 OwooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina madinajicita niЙЎМ¶ina ЙЎМ¶aniotagodi makaami liotagipi, niЙЎМ¶ina ane iwaЙЎМ¶atitiwaji odaa jiЙЎМ¶iniaa ane ЙЎМ¶adiiЙЎМ¶eni. Yakadi me awiitetiwaji ane beyagi, pida baЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adelewi, codaa idiokaanaЙЎМ¶a limedi me leegitalo motonitedice AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. OЙЎМ¶oa domige iwaЙЎМ¶ati AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa dibatedaЙЎМ¶agitiwaji, codaa eote me ЙЎМ¶adeЙЎМ¶enakitiwaji.
\v 17 NiЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide akaami liotagipi nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a, codaa adomaЙЎМ¶akati mikani. Pida iniotagodeeЙЎМ¶atalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iwaЙЎМ¶atitetiwaji catiwedi ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶ena niЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco anoditece ЙЎМ¶otiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi anetiЙЎМ¶adiiЙЎМ¶axinitece.
\v 18 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me yajigotedaЙЎМ¶awa ЙЎМ¶adoniciwaЙЎМ¶a mikani mawii ane beyagi. Odaa jaЙЎМ¶adinajicitalo makaami liotagipi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji mawii ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 19 ЗӨadotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶enitiwaji micataЙЎМ¶a okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica oko jaotibige me jakadi me ЙЎМ¶adaxawani mowooЙЎМ¶oti ane jemaa mejitaЙЎМ¶awa, leeЙЎМ¶odi aЙЎМ¶adoniciwati me iwaЙЎМ¶atakani. NiЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide adinajicitiwaji manigopeliЙЎМ¶itiwage, awiite inoatawece ane deЙЎМ¶eleteda, codaa aЙЎМ¶alee domaЙЎМ¶akati mikani mawii ane beyagi. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina natigide jaЙЎМ¶adinajicitiwaji makaami liotaka AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji mawii ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaa miniokaaЙЎМ¶iniwateda makaami nepilidi.
\p 
\v 20 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo maleeЙЎМ¶akaami liotagipi nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a, aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adowoogotiwaji daЙЎМ¶awii niЙЎМ¶ica ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a aiiЙЎМ¶e ЙЎМ¶adewiЙЎМ¶a.
\v 21 Amiini ica ЙЎМ¶anigaanyetema ijoa ЙЎМ¶adoenataka ane beyagi? NiЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶adoenataka ane beyagi owo manibolikitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina natigide, codaa niЙЎМ¶ina ane beyagi owo oko me yeleo, odaa idiokaanaЙЎМ¶a limedi me leegitalo me yototedice AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 22 Pida niЙЎМ¶ina natigide AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja yajigotedaЙЎМ¶awa ЙЎМ¶adoniciwaЙЎМ¶a mikani mawii ane beyagi, odaa jaЙЎМ¶akaami liotagipi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Odaa iniokaaniЙЎМ¶iniwateda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji makaami nepilidi. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi midiokaanaЙЎМ¶a limedi me ЙЎМ¶adewikitiwaji MiniwataЙЎМ¶a.
\v 23 LeeЙЎМ¶odi loojedi nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a ane jibaЙЎМ¶atege baЙЎМ¶a nГ©maЙЎМ¶a, odaa idiokaanaЙЎМ¶a limedi me leegitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me jotonaЙЎМ¶atedice. Pida liboonigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane najigotedoЙЎМ¶owa baЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶a ane daЙЎМ¶adiaaЙЎМ¶ica liniogo MiniwataЙЎМ¶a, leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo loenatagitedoЙЎМ¶odomi ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus Cristo.
\c 7
\s1 NadoneЙЎМ¶egi ane ЙЎМ¶odiiЙЎМ¶axitece
\p 
\v 1 Inioxoadipi. Akaamitawece joЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶oti anejatigi igegi leeЙЎМ¶odi owooЙЎМ¶oti niЙЎМ¶ijoa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. NiЙЎМ¶ina oko leeditibige me diotece niЙЎМ¶inoa niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco niЙЎМ¶ina malee yewiЙЎМ¶a.
\v 2 Liciagi naЙЎМ¶ana iwaalo wadonaЙЎМ¶a. NiiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi wadonadi iiЙЎМ¶e me iniokini mida aneetege niЙЎМ¶ini lodawa niЙЎМ¶ina malee yewiЙЎМ¶a. Pida nige yeleo niЙЎМ¶ijo lodawa, odaa naЙЎМ¶ani iwaalo ja iwoko niЙЎМ¶ijo niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi wadonadi ane yexocaЙЎМ¶aditege lodawa.
\v 3 Pida naЙЎМ¶ani iwaalo nige lodawa eledi ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa malee yewiЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo baЙЎМ¶a lodawa, odaa naЙЎМ¶ani iwaalo baЙЎМ¶a doЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶ataka. Pida nige yeleo niЙЎМ¶ijo lodawa, odaa ja iwoko niЙЎМ¶ijo niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi me wadonaЙЎМ¶alo. Odaa ja yakaditace me wado, aЙЎМ¶alee doЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶ataka.
\p 
\v 4 Inioxoadipi, joaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eetiwaji. NaЙЎМ¶ana iwaalo iwoko niЙЎМ¶ijo niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi me wadonaЙЎМ¶alo, leeЙЎМ¶odi naЙЎМ¶a yeleo lodawa. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a enitiwaji ЙЎМ¶adiwokoni niЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco ane nadeegi MoisГ©s, leeЙЎМ¶odi naЙЎМ¶a micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶ademaЙЎМ¶awa Cristo. Odaa jaЙЎМ¶akatitiwaji mida anenitege NiЙЎМ¶ijoa ane yeleo, pida yewiЙЎМ¶atace niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi, eotedibige me jakataЙЎМ¶a me jaoЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yemaa.
\v 5 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo malee ЙЎМ¶odiiЙЎМ¶e ЙЎМ¶olidaЙЎМ¶ataka ane beyagi, odaa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji joЙЎМ¶owo me jowooЙЎМ¶atibige ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a. Pida niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶olidaЙЎМ¶ataka owo mepaanaЙЎМ¶a jaoЙЎМ¶a ane beyagi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶obeyaceЙЎМ¶eco etiЙЎМ¶odadeegita ЙЎМ¶odemaЙЎМ¶a, odaa idiokaanaЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a limedi me jotonaЙЎМ¶atedice AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 6 MacataЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶ana wajekalo naЙЎМ¶a iwoko niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi me wadonaЙЎМ¶alo, oko jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ejinaЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶alee leeditibige daЙЎМ¶a jiwaЙЎМ¶atece niЙЎМ¶ijoa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji anijo mida loniciwaЙЎМ¶atoЙЎМ¶oloco. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi aЙЎМ¶alee jibaaЙЎМ¶atema AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji anejinaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide me jiwaЙЎМ¶atece niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco ane diniditedini. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina natigide jibaaЙЎМ¶atema AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me gela anejinaЙЎМ¶a me ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶a ane najigotoЙЎМ¶owa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo.
\s1 JeЙЎМ¶epaanaЙЎМ¶a jaoЙЎМ¶a ane beyagi niЙЎМ¶ina naЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a jowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji
\p 
\v 7 Domige yakadi mejinaЙЎМ¶a inoa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me beyagi? Ayakadi diЙЎМ¶ideЙЎМ¶ejalaЙЎМ¶atigi ЙЎМ¶ogegi! IgaataЙЎМ¶a liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji onikeetoЙЎМ¶owa nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a. IgaataЙЎМ¶a daaditoЙЎМ¶odita niЙЎМ¶inoa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco me beyagi niЙЎМ¶ina me idocetema niЙЎМ¶inoa ane nepilidi eledi oko. AgotaЙЎМ¶a jowooЙЎМ¶odi me beyagi, niЙЎМ¶ina me jemaa ane nebi eledi oko.
\v 8 Pida leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶inoa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji (me jowooЙЎМ¶odi ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a), odaa nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a ane idei catiwedi yaaleЙЎМ¶ena jeЙЎМ¶eo me idocetema ane nebi eledi oko. IgaataЙЎМ¶a daaditiЙЎМ¶icoateda niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco, nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a ane idei catiwedi yaaleЙЎМ¶ena taЙЎМ¶a liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina Г©meЙЎМ¶egi.
\v 9 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide emeЙЎМ¶eeta ajowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶inoa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa eetibece ele, idinitibeci. Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a jowooЙЎМ¶odi ane diitigilo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco, odaa nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a ane idei catiwedi yaaleЙЎМ¶ena ja micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a gela mini, joaniЙЎМ¶ijaaЙЎМ¶ijotigi naЙЎМ¶a jeemitetece minoa ibeyaceЙЎМ¶eco. Odaa ja micataЙЎМ¶a daantaЙЎМ¶a ideleo.
\v 10 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji najigotedoЙЎМ¶owa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco mowo ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶a. Pida niЙЎМ¶idiwa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco ododigotiwa micataЙЎМ¶a daantaЙЎМ¶a ideleo.
\v 11 NibeyacaЙЎМ¶a ane idei catiwedi yaaleЙЎМ¶ena ibake niЙЎМ¶ijoa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me idinaale. IgaataЙЎМ¶a jiletibige diЙЎМ¶idokidata niЙЎМ¶ina me jotete AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco oditaЙЎМ¶a jiЙЎМ¶ida yewiЙЎМ¶a ane daЙЎМ¶adiaaЙЎМ¶ica liniogo. MicataЙЎМ¶a nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a ane idei catiwedi yaaleЙЎМ¶ena daЙЎМ¶a ibake AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco me ideloadi.
\p 
\v 12 NiЙЎМ¶inoa niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco oikee anodaaЙЎМ¶eeteda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, onidatecibeci liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi ikee anodaaЙЎМ¶eeteda. Codaa onidatecibeci liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi ewi, codaa mele.
\v 13 Enice, domigina anele ideloadi? Odaa aleeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco mideЙЎМ¶eji micataЙЎМ¶a Г©meЙЎМ¶egi, pida leeЙЎМ¶odi nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a ane idei catiwedi yaaleЙЎМ¶ena. NiЙЎМ¶ijo nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a ane idei catiwedi yaaleЙЎМ¶ena ibake liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji anele meo me jeemitetece me leegitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me jototedice. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa naЙЎМ¶a dinikee niЙЎМ¶ica anodaaЙЎМ¶ee nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a. Codaa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ikee me daЙЎМ¶axa me beyagi niЙЎМ¶ina nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a.
\s1 Paulo aЙЎМ¶ica loniciwaЙЎМ¶a meo anele
\p 
\v 14 JowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a me AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo ane najigotoЙЎМ¶owa niЙЎМ¶inoa niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco. Pida niЙЎМ¶ida me ee eemoda oko aЙЎМ¶amaleЙЎМ¶egi, codaa ee liotagi nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a, aЙЎМ¶ica inimaweneЙЎМ¶egi daЙЎМ¶a jika me jao ane beyagi.
\v 15 AjowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica aneji. IgaataЙЎМ¶a ajao niЙЎМ¶ina ane jemaa me jao, pida jao inokina ane daЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a jemaa me joe.
\v 16 Pida niЙЎМ¶ina me jaote niЙЎМ¶ina ane beyagi ane daЙЎМ¶a jemaa, jiЙЎМ¶inaa ikee me jowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶inoa niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco mele.
\v 17 NiЙЎМ¶ina me jao niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a jemaa, eledi ikee maleedeЙЎМ¶emeЙЎМ¶ee ane jao, pida loniciwaЙЎМ¶a nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a ane idei catiwedi yaaleЙЎМ¶ena idiiЙЎМ¶e me jao niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a jemaa.
\v 18 IgaataЙЎМ¶a jowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ina anele aЙЎМ¶ica meetaЙЎМ¶a catiwedi yaaleЙЎМ¶ena. IdaaЙЎМ¶ee daЙЎМ¶a jemaa me jao anele, pida aЙЎМ¶ica inimaweneЙЎМ¶egi daЙЎМ¶a jao.
\v 19 IgaataЙЎМ¶a ajaote anele ane jemaa me jao, pida jao ane beyagi ane daЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a jemaa me jao.
\v 20 Nige jao niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a jemaa me jao, aneЙЎМ¶emeЙЎМ¶ee ane jao, pida loniciwaЙЎМ¶a nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a ane idei catiwedi yaaleЙЎМ¶ena idiiЙЎМ¶e me jao.
\p 
\v 21 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa midatibece meji catiwedi yaaleЙЎМ¶ena. NiЙЎМ¶ina me domaЙЎМ¶a jemaa me jao anele, pida inoka jakadi me joletibige niЙЎМ¶ica ane beyagi.
\v 22 IgaataЙЎМ¶a emeЙЎМ¶eeta domaЙЎМ¶a jemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco.
\v 23 Pida jeemiteta noniciwaЙЎМ¶a ilaligi, ane idei catiwedi yaaleЙЎМ¶ena. NiЙЎМ¶ida noniciwaЙЎМ¶a micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a ideleЙЎМ¶e liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane jemaa. NiЙЎМ¶ida noniciwaЙЎМ¶a idiiЙЎМ¶e me jao ane beyagi, odaa aЙЎМ¶ica emaЙЎМ¶a yoniciwaЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a jika me jao ane beyagi.
\v 24 Ee oko anidioka limedi magecaЙЎМ¶alo! Migica ane yakadi me idoЙЎМ¶atice midataЙЎМ¶a ida noniciwaЙЎМ¶a ane idadeegita nГ©maЙЎМ¶a, codaa aneo midiokaanaЙЎМ¶a limedi me leegitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me jototedice?
\v 25 Iniotagodetalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, leeЙЎМ¶odi ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus Cristo jiЙЎМ¶iniaa idoЙЎМ¶atedice mejoteloco loniciwaЙЎМ¶a nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a.
\p NiЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide me yowoogo me jotete liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Pida inoka jao ane beyagi, leeЙЎМ¶odi loniciwaЙЎМ¶a nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a.
\c 8
\s1 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo najigotoЙЎМ¶owa ЙЎМ¶odoniciwaЙЎМ¶a
\p 
\v 1 Ja jinataЙЎМ¶a ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus Cristo me ЙЎМ¶odoЙЎМ¶atedice mejonaЙЎМ¶ateloco loniciwaЙЎМ¶a nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aЙЎМ¶alee ЙЎМ¶odiloikatidi leeЙЎМ¶otedi ЙЎМ¶obeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, oko ane ЙЎМ¶odexogotege Jesus Cristo, ane daЙЎМ¶adiaa iniwinaЙЎМ¶atalo epaa lidekeco ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena, pida jibaaЙЎМ¶atema Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 2 IgaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo najigotoЙЎМ¶owa gela ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi me ЙЎМ¶odexogotege Jesus Cristo. Odaa loniciwaЙЎМ¶a Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЙЎМ¶odoЙЎМ¶atice mejonaЙЎМ¶ateloco loniciwaЙЎМ¶a nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a ane nadeegi ЙЎМ¶odemaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 3 AjakataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a jaaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a ane idei catiwedi ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena daЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi me jotetenaЙЎМ¶a liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niiЙЎМ¶e epaa Lionigi aneote me ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa digo mokotaЙЎМ¶a, pida baadiЙЎМ¶icata libeyaceЙЎМ¶egi. Niwakatee Lionigi me yaaЙЎМ¶adi ЙЎМ¶obeyacaЙЎМ¶a, eote lawikodigi Lionigi leeЙЎМ¶odi ЙЎМ¶obeyacaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 4 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niiЙЎМ¶e Lionigi me yeleotedoЙЎМ¶odomi, eotedibige mida ЙЎМ¶onimaweneЙЎМ¶egi me jaoЙЎМ¶a ane niiЙЎМ¶etoЙЎМ¶owa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a. Natigide aЙЎМ¶alee jaoЙЎМ¶a ane okomaЙЎМ¶a jemaanaЙЎМ¶a me jaoЙЎМ¶a, pida jaoЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina ane niiЙЎМ¶etoЙЎМ¶owa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo.
\p 
\v 5 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina anowo anepaa lidekeco laaleЙЎМ¶ena, inokina moyowo mowo. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina anowo ane yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo, idioka limedi moyowo niЙЎМ¶ica ane iiЙЎМ¶etiogi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo.
\v 6 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina aninoka oyowo anepaa yemaa laaleЙЎМ¶ena mowo, joaniЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi biЙЎМ¶idiokaanaЙЎМ¶a limedi moyototedice AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nige nigo. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina anoyowo niЙЎМ¶ica ane yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo, biЙЎМ¶idiokaanaЙЎМ¶a limedi me newiЙЎМ¶a MiniwataЙЎМ¶a, codaa midioka limedi mele laaleЙЎМ¶enali.
\v 7 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina aninoka yowoteda lakataЙЎМ¶a ane beyagi ane yemaa laaleЙЎМ¶ena, joaniЙЎМ¶iniaa laxakawa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa aЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yakadi meniwaЙЎМ¶atakanaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 8 NiЙЎМ¶ina anodioteci epaa lidaЙЎМ¶ataka laaleЙЎМ¶ena, aЙЎМ¶ica nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi doЙЎМ¶oyocaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\p 
\v 9 Odaa akaamitiwaji ane diЙЎМ¶iwaЙЎМ¶ati niЙЎМ¶inoa anepaa yemaa ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali, pida naЙЎМ¶a iwaЙЎМ¶ati AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo, jiЙЎМ¶ikeeni mewi me diЙЎМ¶eladetiwaЙЎМ¶aji AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo. Nige diЙЎМ¶icata Cristo Liwigo minitaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ini oko, niЙЎМ¶ini oko anebi Cristo.
\v 10 Pida Cristo nige itediwaЙЎМ¶ajitiwaji, odaa icaaЙЎМ¶ica nige ЙЎМ¶adelewi leeЙЎМ¶odi nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo yajigotaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji gela ЙЎМ¶adewiЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji jeЙЎМ¶eote me ЙЎМ¶odeЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 11 Codaa nige itiwaЙЎМ¶ajitiwaji AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo, niЙЎМ¶ijo aneo Jesus me yewiЙЎМ¶atace, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, aneote Cristo me yewiЙЎМ¶atace, aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶eote me ЙЎМ¶adewikitace, codaa eote gela ЙЎМ¶adolaadi, leeЙЎМ¶odi Liwigo ane itiwaЙЎМ¶ajitiwaji.
\p 
\v 12 Enice inioxoadipi, jinaЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a jiwaЙЎМ¶atece anepaa lidaЙЎМ¶ataka ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶enali.
\v 13 IgaataЙЎМ¶a nige iwitecetiwaji ane lidaЙЎМ¶ataka ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali, aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶awienatakanitiwaji me ЙЎМ¶adelewi, codaa midiokaanaЙЎМ¶a limedi motonitedice AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Pida Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yakadi me yajigotaЙЎМ¶awa ЙЎМ¶animaweneЙЎМ¶egi me ikani mawii niЙЎМ¶inoa anakamaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶alidaЙЎМ¶ataka mawiite. Odaa nigikani mawiite niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali lidekeco ane beyagi, odaa idiokaanaЙЎМ¶a limedi me ЙЎМ¶adewikitiwaji miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\p 
\v 14 IgaataЙЎМ¶a inatawece niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane iiЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo, joaniЙЎМ¶idiaa lionigipi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 15 IgaataЙЎМ¶a adakatiwoЙЎМ¶oji niwigo aneo moko ageleemagipi. Pida jibaЙЎМ¶atege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo aneo me dibatedoЙЎМ¶owa moko lionigipi, codaa eo me japaawaЙЎМ¶atibige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji mejinaЙЎМ¶a, вҖңEiodi, Eiodi yemaanigi!вҖқ
\v 16 Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eledi meetoЙЎМ¶owa catiwedi ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena moko lionigipi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 17 LeeЙЎМ¶odi moko lionigipi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa ane nebi, oko aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶onebi. NiЙЎМ¶ica AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji laЙЎМ¶ajegitetema Cristo, odaa oko ЙЎМ¶onedianaЙЎМ¶awa nige limedi me dibatetege niЙЎМ¶ica naЙЎМ¶ajegi. IgaataЙЎМ¶a nige jawikodeeЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi me jibaaЙЎМ¶atema Cristo, digo mijoataЙЎМ¶a me dawikode, odaa oko jawanaЙЎМ¶atege nigoiweniЙЎМ¶ide.
\s1 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji doЙЎМ¶etetedoЙЎМ¶owa
\p 
\v 18 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶odawikodico digoina iiЙЎМ¶o, ejidaЙЎМ¶a yakadi daЙЎМ¶a jiboЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶atege niЙЎМ¶ica AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji anicota me najigotedoЙЎМ¶owa, anicota me nikeetedoЙЎМ¶owa, nige limedi me doЙЎМ¶etetedibigoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 19 IgaataЙЎМ¶a inoatawece ane liidaЙЎМ¶atajedi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji onibeotege codaa eliodi moyemaa me age niЙЎМ¶ica noko nige yeloЙЎМ¶otee lionaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 20-21 IgaataЙЎМ¶a inoatawece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liidaЙЎМ¶atajedi jiЙЎМ¶ijo me diЙЎМ¶ica jaoЙЎМ¶ate. AleeЙЎМ¶odi deЙЎМ¶epaaЙЎМ¶oyemaa me liciagi, pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yemaa migote. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote me inibeoonaЙЎМ¶atege micota noko meote me daЙЎМ¶adiaa yeleo okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶inoa ane liidaЙЎМ¶atajegi. Codaa aЙЎМ¶alee neladi, pida inoatawece ja iwoko lawikodico, odaa ja ninitibigiwaji lodoe AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, digo mokotaЙЎМ¶a anoko lionigipi.
\p 
\v 22 MacataЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶ana iwaalo baanaЙЎМ¶a nikaticobece laadi naЙЎМ¶a dineemite me nipegi menitini lionigi ane nibeotege. JiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee, inoatawece ane AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liidaЙЎМ¶atajedi aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a onikaticobece laadi niЙЎМ¶ina monibeotege niЙЎМ¶ica noko nige dibatedoЙЎМ¶ogi anoko lionigipi.
\v 23 AЙЎМ¶inokinoa eletidi liidaЙЎМ¶atajedi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meneЙЎМ¶egi onikaticobece laadi niЙЎМ¶ina monibeotege niЙЎМ¶ica noko. Pida oko baanaЙЎМ¶a jibaЙЎМ¶atege Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, anodoejegi ЙЎМ¶onoЙЎМ¶eeditalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, oko aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a eliodi me inikanaЙЎМ¶aticobece ЙЎМ¶odaadi niЙЎМ¶ina me inibeoonaЙЎМ¶atege niЙЎМ¶ica noko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nige dibatedoЙЎМ¶ogi anoko lionigipi, odaa jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a jibaЙЎМ¶atege gela ЙЎМ¶odolaadi.
\v 24 InibeoonaЙЎМ¶atege gela ЙЎМ¶odolaadi leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ida gela ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶a. Nige naЙЎМ¶a jinataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ica ane inibeoonaЙЎМ¶atege, odaa aЙЎМ¶alee leeditibige daЙЎМ¶a inibeoonaЙЎМ¶atege, igaataЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶ica ane nibeotege niЙЎМ¶ina baanaЙЎМ¶a eliodi me nadi.
\v 25 Pida nige inibeoonaЙЎМ¶atege niЙЎМ¶ica ane diЙЎМ¶ica me jinataЙЎМ¶a, leeditibige me idinatiiЙЎМ¶atalo ЙЎМ¶odawikodico niЙЎМ¶ina me inibeoonaЙЎМ¶atege.
\p 
\v 26 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odaxawa, leeЙЎМ¶odi aЙЎМ¶ica ЙЎМ¶odoniciwaЙЎМ¶a. Codaa ajowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ica anodaaЙЎМ¶ee me jotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo me dipokotoЙЎМ¶oloco. Codaa dinoniciwaЙЎМ¶adi me dipokotoЙЎМ¶oloco, ajakataЙЎМ¶a me jeloЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ica anodaaЙЎМ¶ee me dipokotoЙЎМ¶oloco, pida baЙЎМ¶a jeemiteeЙЎМ¶atece catiwedi ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena.
\v 27 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji naditediwece catiwedi laaleЙЎМ¶ena oko, codaa yowooЙЎМ¶odi lowooko Liwigo. IgaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo niЙЎМ¶ina me dipokoteloco loiigi, inoka dipokota ane yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\p 
\v 28 JowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ibake inoatawece niЙЎМ¶inoa ane ЙЎМ¶oninyaco meote aneletema niЙЎМ¶ina oko anoyemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, aneniditediogi me lionigipi, anakaa lowoogotetece.
\v 29 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji baanaЙЎМ¶a iolatedicoace, iomaЙЎМ¶aditedicoace meote me liciagi Lionigi. Eotedibige Lionigi me liidaЙЎМ¶a liwigotigilo eliodi nioxoadipi.
\v 30 NiЙЎМ¶ina ane iomaЙЎМ¶aditedicoace, eniditediogi me lionigipi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina aneniditediogi, jeЙЎМ¶eote me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶adi, iweniЙЎМ¶ide yawanaЙЎМ¶aditetege Cristo.
\s1 Ica anodaaЙЎМ¶ee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ЙЎМ¶odemaa
\p 
\v 31 Ja jinataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me dibatedoЙЎМ¶owa moko lionigipi, codaa me ЙЎМ¶odaxawa, odaa domigica ane yakadi me ЙЎМ¶odiЙЎМ¶eke?
\v 32 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ayoli Lionigi, pida yajigo me yeleotedoЙЎМ¶odomi. JinataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me yajigo epaa Lionigi, odaa jowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a me najigotedoЙЎМ¶owa me ЙЎМ¶onoЙЎМ¶etedi inoatawece niЙЎМ¶inoa ane jopooЙЎМ¶atibige.
\v 33 Domigica ane yakadi me laagetedipi liomaЙЎМ¶ataka AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji? AЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi. LeeЙЎМ¶odi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yeloЙЎМ¶odi me diЙЎМ¶icata libatiigi niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi.
\v 34 Domigica ane yakadi me ЙЎМ¶odiloikatidi leeЙЎМ¶odi ЙЎМ¶obeyaceЙЎМ¶eco? AЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi, leeЙЎМ¶odi Cristo ja yeleotedoЙЎМ¶odomi, codaa me yewiЙЎМ¶atace, odaa etiniwa liwai libaaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, dipokotedoЙЎМ¶oloco miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 35 Odaa, domigica ane yakadi me ЙЎМ¶odawalacetege Cristo ane ЙЎМ¶odemaa? Domige ЙЎМ¶odawikodico, oЙЎМ¶oa domige inoa ЙЎМ¶odaЙЎМ¶alanaЙЎМ¶a, oЙЎМ¶oa domige ina metiЙЎМ¶odiatetibeci, oЙЎМ¶oa domige nigigi, oЙЎМ¶oa domige ina maniaditibige ЙЎМ¶odowoodaЙЎМ¶agi, oЙЎМ¶oa domige ina mida ane idoiiЙЎМ¶ata, oЙЎМ¶oa domige ina modoletibige metiЙЎМ¶odeloadi; inoatawece inoa ganicinoa, domigoyakadi metiЙЎМ¶odawalacetege Cristo? Ee meji aЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi.
\v 36 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa aneeta AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi,
\q1 вҖңAkaami leeЙЎМ¶odi,
\q1 inoatawece nokododi odoletibige metiЙЎМ¶odeloadi.
\q1 OdodigotoЙЎМ¶owa micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina waxacoco anoyadeegiticogi nematakanaЙЎМ¶axi.вҖқ
\p 
\v 37 Pida ja ЙЎМ¶odixomaЙЎМ¶atema inoatawece ane ЙЎМ¶oninyaco, odaa aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica ane ЙЎМ¶odakadi, leeЙЎМ¶odi Cristo me ЙЎМ¶odemaa.
\v 38-39 IgaataЙЎМ¶a jowooЙЎМ¶odi, codaa ajawienataka me diЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi me ЙЎМ¶odawalacetege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane ЙЎМ¶odemaa. OteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a nГ©maЙЎМ¶a ayakadi, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶a, migetaЙЎМ¶a aanjotedi, migetaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶icoa ane niiЙЎМ¶enatakanaЙЎМ¶a digoida ditibigimedi, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶icoa niwicidi ane daЙЎМ¶axa me notoetedi, migetaЙЎМ¶a anigetiЙЎМ¶ida ЙЎМ¶oninyaagi niЙЎМ¶ina natigide, migetaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶oninyaagi anigida noko, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a gaantokaaЙЎМ¶idi ane idei ditibigimedi, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a aninoa digoina iiЙЎМ¶o, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a anigetiЙЎМ¶idi niЙЎМ¶inoa eletidi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji loenataka. AЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi me ЙЎМ¶odawalacetege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane ЙЎМ¶odemaa. Codaa ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus Cristo ja ikee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meliodi me ЙЎМ¶odemaa.
\c 9
\s1 Noiigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane iolatedice
\p 
\v 1 Ejitece anewi leeЙЎМ¶odi ee nebi Cristo. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo eo me jowooЙЎМ¶odi me jao ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa nikeetiwa me daЙЎМ¶a jiwitaka.
\v 2 Eliodi me ee agecaЙЎМ¶alo, jilee yaaleЙЎМ¶ena codaa aliditini, leeЙЎМ¶odi emaЙЎМ¶a yoiigi. (Ee agecaЙЎМ¶alo leeЙЎМ¶odi modowocetege ane domiЙЎМ¶igotediogi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶adi).
\v 3 EmeЙЎМ¶eeta domeЙЎМ¶elioditibece me jemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji daЙЎМ¶a idixoo, codaa daЙЎМ¶a idawalacetetege Cristo leeЙЎМ¶odi yoiigi, migetaЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yaxawa.
\v 4 Yoiigi, loiigi Israel. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji iomaЙЎМ¶aditedicoace meote me lionigipi, codaa me dinikeetediogi anodaaЙЎМ¶eeteda. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja ikeetediogi ane yemaa migote loiigi, codaa me yajigotediogi liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja ikeetediogi anodaaЙЎМ¶ee modoЙЎМ¶etetalo minitaЙЎМ¶a liЙЎМ¶eladi, codaa eote ligegitetege.
\v 5 NiЙЎМ¶idi noiigi ida aneetege licoЙЎМ¶egi jotigide ЙЎМ¶odaamipi, ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, ane dinikeetediogi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Cristo ida aneetetege licoЙЎМ¶egi miditaЙЎМ¶a, codaa inaaЙЎМ¶ina niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi. IjaaЙЎМ¶ijoa Cristo ЗӨonoenoЙЎМ¶odi, iiЙЎМ¶e inoatawece. Inatawece oko domaЙЎМ¶a leeditibige midioka limedi modoЙЎМ¶etetalo. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee. (AmГ©m.)
\p 
\v 6 Pida aЙЎМ¶eji me diЙЎМ¶icota ane ligegi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. IgaataЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶inatawece loiigi Israel iomaЙЎМ¶aditedice AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me loiigi.
\v 7 Codaa aЙЎМ¶inatawece anida aneetege licoЙЎМ¶egi mijotaЙЎМ¶a AbraГЈo ewi me lionigipi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. IgaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meeteta AbraГЈo, вҖңInokina anida aneetege licoЙЎМ¶egi ЙЎМ¶adionigi Isaque, beЙЎМ¶ejitiogi mida aneetege ЙЎМ¶adicoЙЎМ¶egi.вҖқ
\v 8 Digawini ane diitigi, nigaanigipawaanigi ane lanikadi miditaЙЎМ¶a noiigi Israel, aЙЎМ¶inatawece lionigipi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Pida inokina mida aneetege licoЙЎМ¶egi AbraГЈo niЙЎМ¶ina anenitini leeЙЎМ¶odi me ligegi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, inokina me dibatetege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji mewi me loiigi.
\v 9 LeeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote niЙЎМ¶ida ligegitetege AbraГЈo, вҖңNigeledi nicaaЙЎМ¶abi, idopitacijo, odaa Sara jiЙЎМ¶icaa lionigi.вҖқ
\p 
\v 10 Pida aniЙЎМ¶idokidata. Rebeca ijoa itoataale lionaЙЎМ¶a ijokijota naniodi, ЙЎМ¶onelokodi Isaque.
\v 11-12 Pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ikee me iolatedice oko ane yemaa me iolatedice, odaa meeteta Rebeca, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ica liidaЙЎМ¶a, liotagi niЙЎМ¶ica loxooxegi.вҖқ AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote ligegitetege niЙЎМ¶ijo maleediЙЎМ¶icatibige deЙЎМ¶enitiniwace niЙЎМ¶ijo nigaanigipawaanigi, maleediЙЎМ¶ica doЙЎМ¶oyakadi mowote gaantiЙЎМ¶ini anele, migetaЙЎМ¶a ane beyagi. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ikee me iolatedice oko leeЙЎМ¶odi mepaa yemaa meniditeta, idiЙЎМ¶ida aleeЙЎМ¶odi ane loenataka niЙЎМ¶ina oko.
\v 13 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eeta lotaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me diniditeloco,
\q1 вҖңJemaa JacГі,
\q1 pida yeleЙЎМ¶edi EsaГә.вҖқ
\p 
\v 14 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji domige iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a ina me iolatedicoace ina oko anepaa yemaa? Ayakadi diЙЎМ¶ideЙЎМ¶ejalaЙЎМ¶atigi ЙЎМ¶ogegi!
\v 15 IgaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meeteta MoisГ©s, вҖңJiwikode niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane jemaa me jiwikode. Codaa jao me Ee eletema niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane jemaa me Ee eletema.вҖқ
\v 16 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji iolatedice oko aleeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ina oko miniaa yemaa, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi ane loenataka. Pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji iolatedice oko leeЙЎМ¶odi me iwikode.
\v 17 IgaataЙЎМ¶a diniditeloco lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ijo ligegite FaraГі, meeteta, вҖңJoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi me jao makaami inionigi-eliodi, jaotibige me jikee inimaweneЙЎМ¶egitece niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶aninyaagi, codaa me jaotibige minatawece oko digoina iiЙЎМ¶o oyowooЙЎМ¶odi IboonaЙЎМ¶adi.вҖқ
\v 18 Odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji iwikode niЙЎМ¶ina ane yemaa me iwikode, yakakaЙЎМ¶adi laaleЙЎМ¶ena niЙЎМ¶ina ane yemaa me yakakaЙЎМ¶adi laaleЙЎМ¶ena.
\s1 Inatecibece oko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji iwikode, inaaЙЎМ¶eledi baЙЎМ¶a iloikatidi
\p 
\v 19 Yakadi mini niЙЎМ¶ina akaamitiwaji aneetiwa, вҖңNige niЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee, amica ane yakadi me dakapetege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yemaa, enice igaamee ina AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji malee dilaagetete oko?вҖқ
\v 20 Pida yokaaЙЎМ¶edi. NiЙЎМ¶ida makaami minakaamita oko. Odaa aЙЎМ¶akati daЙЎМ¶adinotigimadenitege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina ane noenatagi ayakadi deЙЎМ¶eeta niЙЎМ¶ina noenatagodi, вҖңIgaamee ina mideЙЎМ¶emiitiwa madoeni?вҖқ
\v 21 NiЙЎМ¶ina niwilanaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a ane iwila boote ida nimaweneЙЎМ¶egitece me iwila ane yemaa migota me iwila napaloaЙЎМ¶a. Yakadi meo boote ane daЙЎМ¶axa me libiniena, oЙЎМ¶oa migeo naЙЎМ¶ana boote ane daЙЎМ¶a libiniena anoibaketema okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica. Pida iniokini niЙЎМ¶ini napaloaЙЎМ¶a ane iwila. \fig |src="HK00140B.TIF" size="span" copy="Horace Knowles revised by Louise Bass В© The British & Foreign Bible Society, 1994." ref="Romanos 9.21"\fig*
\p 
\v 22 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee. Yemaa me ikee lГ©laЙЎМ¶atetema nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a, codaa yemaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko moyowooЙЎМ¶odi nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi. Eliodi me dinatite, codaa me ikee me yakadi me ixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedijo loenataka niЙЎМ¶ijo oko ane yelatetema, joaniЙЎМ¶idiaa naaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 23 Codaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yemaa me ikee meliodi loniciwaЙЎМ¶a meote me ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶a codaa ЙЎМ¶odiweniЙЎМ¶ide digo minataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko anicota minatawece oiweniЙЎМ¶ide. Jotigide naЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odiwikode, codaa me ЙЎМ¶odeyaЙЎМ¶adi me ЙЎМ¶odinelecaЙЎМ¶atee, codaa modoЙЎМ¶etetibigoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 24 IgaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eniditedoЙЎМ¶owa, aЙЎМ¶inokina niЙЎМ¶ina ane judeutedi, pida eledi eniditediogi niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi.
\p 
\v 25 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eete AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane iditini OsГ©ias, anee,
\q1 вҖңNiЙЎМ¶idi ane daЙЎМ¶a yoiigi,
\q1 icota mejitiogi me, вҖҳYoiigiвҖҷ.
\q1 Codaa noiigi ane daЙЎМ¶a jemaa,
\q1 icota mejitiogi me, вҖҳYemaanigipi.вҖҷвҖқ
\q1 
\v 26 IdiaaЙЎМ¶idi niЙЎМ¶ica nipodigi neЙЎМ¶eetediogi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ica oko,
\q1 вҖңAЙЎМ¶akaamitiwaji yoiigiвҖқ,
\q1 idiaaЙЎМ¶itace nigoditiogi,
\q1 вҖңLionigipi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ewikegi.вҖқ
\p 
\v 27 IsaГӯas yalaЙЎМ¶ata loiigi Israel, niЙЎМ¶ijo mee, вҖңDiganee loiigi Israel meliodi, micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina dotiwadi liniogotibece akiidi-eliodi. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote lewiЙЎМ¶a onateciЙЎМ¶idi niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi.
\v 28 IgaataЙЎМ¶a aleegi ЗӨoniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja iloikatidi inatawece noiigi niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o, leeЙЎМ¶odi iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a. Inoatawece niЙЎМ¶inoa aneete ico micotece.вҖқ
\v 29 AniЙЎМ¶icatibige IsaГӯas deЙЎМ¶eetece niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a, niЙЎМ¶ijoa eletidi lotaЙЎМ¶a me yalaЙЎМ¶ata analeeЙЎМ¶icotece, mee, вҖңЗӨoniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane iiЙЎМ¶e inoatawece, daaditiЙЎМ¶ica ane nenyaЙЎМ¶aditetema anida aneetege licoЙЎМ¶egi ЙЎМ¶odaamipi, taЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odiciagi nigotaЙЎМ¶a Sodoma ajaa Gomorra ane yaaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.вҖқ
\s1 Noiigi Israel aЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi nibodicetedi anele ane icoЙЎМ¶otedibigimece miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji
\p 
\v 30 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eniditediogi oko inatawece digawiniteloco ane noiigi. Ja jinataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me dibatetege ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi leeЙЎМ¶odi monakato, ane doЙЎМ¶odoletibige me dibatetege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 31 Pida noiigi Israel anodoletibige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me dibatetege leeЙЎМ¶odi moyotete liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco, pida aЙЎМ¶oyakadi moyotete niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco.
\v 32-33 Igaamee daЙЎМ¶a yakadi me dibatetege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji? Ayakadi leeЙЎМ¶odi odoletibige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me dibatetege leeЙЎМ¶odi moyotete niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi, idiЙЎМ¶ida aleeЙЎМ¶odi doЙЎМ¶onakato AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Odaa micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a nixipaЙЎМ¶a, ixipe wetiЙЎМ¶a. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a eetece naЙЎМ¶ajo wetiЙЎМ¶a, niЙЎМ¶ijo mee,
\q1 вҖңDigawini!
\q1 Jao inikateloco wetiЙЎМ¶a manitaЙЎМ¶a nigotaЙЎМ¶a SiГЈo.
\q1 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko odixipetigi naЙЎМ¶ani wetiЙЎМ¶a.
\q1 NaЙЎМ¶ani wetiЙЎМ¶a nelegi eo niЙЎМ¶ina oko menitiniwace.
\q1 Pida aneyiwaЙЎМ¶adi baadiЙЎМ¶ica liboliЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ
\m (NiЙЎМ¶ijoa liiЙЎМ¶exegi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji jiЙЎМ¶iniaaЙЎМ¶oditalo me wetiЙЎМ¶a.)
\c 10
\p 
\v 1 Inioxoadipi. Jemaa manitawece yaaleЙЎМ¶ena, yoiigi Israel mida lewiЙЎМ¶a. Jipokotalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote lewiЙЎМ¶a.
\v 2 IgaataЙЎМ¶a jakadi meji meliodi moyemaa moyocaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶etibigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, pida aЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica anigetaЙЎМ¶a nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi.
\v 3 AЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica anigote AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ina oko meote me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a. Odoletibige mowo epaa lakatigi, odaa joЙЎМ¶odowocetege niЙЎМ¶ijo anigote AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji oko me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶adi.
\v 4 IgaataЙЎМ¶a Cristo eotedibige me daЙЎМ¶adiaa leeditibige niЙЎМ¶ina oko me yotete liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji oditaЙЎМ¶a ja iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina oko leeditibige midokida me nakato Cristo, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja dibatetege.
\s1 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yakadi meote lewiЙЎМ¶a okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica oko
\p 
\v 5 MoisГ©s yalaЙЎМ¶ata anodaa nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi oko me yakadi me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a lodoe AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, niЙЎМ¶ina meyiwaЙЎМ¶adi niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco. Mee me iditini, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina aneote inoatawece ane AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco, joaniЙЎМ¶iniaa yakadi midioka limedi me yewiЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi meyiwaЙЎМ¶adi niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco.вҖқ
\v 6 Pida niЙЎМ¶ina meetece MoisГ©s niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi me nakato AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, mee, вҖңJinaЙЎМ¶akamaЙЎМ¶a adinigee, deЙЎМ¶eni, вҖҳAmiijo ica ane yakadi migo digoida ditibigimedi?вҖҷвҖқ NiЙЎМ¶ida ЙЎМ¶agikaneЙЎМ¶egi ikee memaani manadeegi Cristo micoЙЎМ¶oteenitedibigimece ditibigimedi, menagi eote me ЙЎМ¶odeЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 7 Eleditace mee MoisГ©s, вҖңOteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a adinigee, deЙЎМ¶eni вҖҳAmiijo ica ane yakadi migo dinikatinece catinedi iiЙЎМ¶o?вҖҷвҖқ NiЙЎМ¶ida ЙЎМ¶agikaneЙЎМ¶egi ikee memaani mawii Cristo me dinawacetedibige liwigotigi Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, menagi eote me ЙЎМ¶odeЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 8 Pida mee MoisГ©s, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶inoa nibodicetedi ane niwakatee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aЙЎМ¶ica laЙЎМ¶aliigi majipaatalo. AkamaЙЎМ¶akaami jeЙЎМ¶enitece niЙЎМ¶inoa nibodicetedi, codaa etidiwa catiwedi ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶ena.вҖқ IjaaЙЎМ¶ijoa niЙЎМ¶ijoa nibodicetedi ane jeloЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶atedibece anoditece ЙЎМ¶otiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi.
\v 9 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eeta niЙЎМ¶ida nibodigi: Nigenita eledi oko Jesus me ЗӨoniotagodi, codaa nige iwaЙЎМ¶ati AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me yewikatiditace me yeleo, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote ЙЎМ¶adewiЙЎМ¶a.
\v 10 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina mewi mejiwaЙЎМ¶atakanaЙЎМ¶a manitawece ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote me ЙЎМ¶odeЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, codaa nigejinaЙЎМ¶atece ЙЎМ¶otiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji jeЙЎМ¶eote me ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶a.
\p 
\v 11 IgaataЙЎМ¶a mee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi, вҖңInatawece niЙЎМ¶ina anonakato ЗӨoniotagodi aЙЎМ¶ica liboliЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ
\v 12 IgaataЙЎМ¶a lodoe AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji inatawece oko diniciamico, ina ane judeutedi, inaaЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi. IgaataЙЎМ¶a iniaaЙЎМ¶iniwa ЗӨoniotagodi, Niotagodi inatawece oko. Codaa eliodi me ibinie inatawece anodipokotalo me yaxawa.
\v 13 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eeta AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi, niЙЎМ¶ijo mee, вҖңInatawece niЙЎМ¶ina anodipokotibige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶iwaaЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote lewiЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ
\p 
\v 14 Pida igame nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi ina oko modipokotalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nige doЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶aditeda? Codaa igame nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi moyiwaЙЎМ¶adi, nige diЙЎМ¶ica mowajipatalo nibodicetedi anele anoditece ЗӨoniotagodi? Codaa igame nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi me najipaaЙЎМ¶a, nige diЙЎМ¶ica ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditiogi niЙЎМ¶inoa nibodicetedi anele anoditece ЗӨoniotagodi?
\v 15 Codaa igame nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi ina oko me yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece nibodicetedi anele nige daЙЎМ¶a liiЙЎМ¶exegiteda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji? JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi mee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi, вҖңDaЙЎМ¶axa mele niЙЎМ¶ina meno ane nadeegi nibodicetedi anele anoditece ЗӨoniotagodi.вҖқ
\p 
\v 16 Pida onateciЙЎМ¶idi oko anodibatege nibodicetedi anele anoditece ЗӨoniotagodi. IgaataЙЎМ¶a ijo mee IsaГӯas, вҖңIniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. AЙЎМ¶ica aneyiwaЙЎМ¶adi ЙЎМ¶odatematigo.вҖқ
\v 17 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko yakadi me nakato ЗӨoniotagodi niЙЎМ¶ina me wajipata natematigo. Pida wajipata natematigo niЙЎМ¶ina mini ane yeloЙЎМ¶odi nibodicetedi anele ane icoЙЎМ¶otedibigimece miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\p 
\v 18 Natigide jigika, meji, вҖңAgodoЙЎМ¶owajipata natematigo?вҖқ Owajipata! Digo aneeta AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi,
\q1 вҖңInatawece oko digoina iiЙЎМ¶o joЙЎМ¶owajipatalo lotaЙЎМ¶a,
\q1 codaa latematigo jiЙЎМ¶icoticogi neЙЎМ¶epaa niЙЎМ¶ica liniogo iiЙЎМ¶o.вҖқ
\p 
\v 19 Pida jigikataci, mejitiogi, вҖңLoiigi Israel, domigoyowooЙЎМ¶oditece ijo natematigo?вҖқ MoisГ©s odoejegi me digitataka niЙЎМ¶ijo neЙЎМ¶eetece aneeteta AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji,
\q1 вҖңJaote manoceetematiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane diЙЎМ¶ica me yeloЙЎМ¶o midi me noiigi.
\q1 Codaa jao me ЙЎМ¶adelatematiwaji noiigi ane diЙЎМ¶icata lixakedi.вҖқ
\p 
\v 20 Odaa IsaГӯas jaЙЎМ¶ani laaleЙЎМ¶ena maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a eetece ane ligegite AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, mee,
\q1 вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina ane doЙЎМ¶odoletibigiji,
\q1 etidakadi.
\q1 Odaa ja idinikeetiogi niЙЎМ¶ina ane doЙЎМ¶odigikatibigiji.вҖқ
\p 
\v 21 Pida IsaГӯas yalaЙЎМ¶ata loiigi Israel, niЙЎМ¶ijo mee, вҖңInoatawece nokododi jipokotiogi yoiigi modopitiwa. Pida aЙЎМ¶etidadiwaЙЎМ¶adi, otigimadadipi.вҖқ
\c 11
\s1 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji iwikode noiigi Israel
\p 
\v 1 Enice jigika, вҖңAneotedoЙЎМ¶oji domige dowocetetege idi epaa loiigi?вҖқ EjitaЙЎМ¶awa adowocetetege. IgaataЙЎМ¶a emeЙЎМ¶eeta ida anejitege loiigi Israel. Ijo anejitege IcoЙЎМ¶egi AbraГЈo, ida anejitege loiigiwepodi Benjamim.
\v 2 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aikatedice loiigi ane iomaЙЎМ¶aditedice niЙЎМ¶ijo maleediЙЎМ¶icatibige daЙЎМ¶a iliidaЙЎМ¶adi inoatawece ane jinataЙЎМ¶a. OwooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ijoa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a anoditece Elias. Elias laagetedipi loiigi niЙЎМ¶ijo meetalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji,
\v 3 вҖңIniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Onigodi niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece ЙЎМ¶adowooko, codaa oyaaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ijoa nameejatedi wetiadi aneite me inigotaЙЎМ¶a eijedi leeЙЎМ¶odi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco oko. JeЙЎМ¶emokaaneЙЎМ¶eeta me ideyaЙЎМ¶atice, pida aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶odoletibige metideloadi.вҖқ
\v 4 Pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji naЙЎМ¶a igidi Elias, meeteta, вҖңJa jotetetomi seete miili ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi ane doЙЎМ¶oyamaЙЎМ¶atedini lokotidi lodoe niwigo Baal, aЙЎМ¶odoЙЎМ¶etetaвҖқ
\v 5 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina natigide idaaЙЎМ¶ee. YeyaЙЎМ¶aticoace onateciЙЎМ¶idi oko analee nepilidi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, ane iomaЙЎМ¶aditedicoace leeЙЎМ¶odi meliodi meletetema.
\v 6 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji iomaЙЎМ¶aditedice oko leeЙЎМ¶odi meliodi meletetema, idiЙЎМ¶ida aleeЙЎМ¶odi diЙЎМ¶inoa niЙЎМ¶icoa loenataka anele aneo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ninitedibece. IgaataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a iomaЙЎМ¶aditedice AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ina oko leeЙЎМ¶otedi loenataka, odaa agotaЙЎМ¶alee yakadi me ikee meliodi meletetema oko niЙЎМ¶ina me iolatedicoace.
\p 
\v 7 Odaa yakadi mejinaЙЎМ¶a noiigi Israel me diЙЎМ¶icata moyakadi niЙЎМ¶ica anodoletibige. OnexaaЙЎМ¶onateciЙЎМ¶idi oko anoyakadi anodoletibige, joaniЙЎМ¶idiaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane iomaЙЎМ¶aditedicoace. IneЙЎМ¶eledi joЙЎМ¶owote me dakake laaleЙЎМ¶enali.
\v 8 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eeta AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a, вҖңAneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eotedibige me daЙЎМ¶a neemiteeЙЎМ¶a micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a niotaЙЎМ¶a, eotedibige me doЙЎМ¶onadi, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a owajipata ica anewi. JiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee niЙЎМ¶idi oko codaa niЙЎМ¶ina noko.вҖқ
\v 9 Davi eledi yalaЙЎМ¶atiogi, mee,
\q1 вҖңJemaa moiloikatiditibigiwaji miditaЙЎМ¶a lalokadi,
\q1 micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ini eijeeЙЎМ¶agi nibakajetegi,
\q1 codaa moigoetiniwace,
\q1 odaa ja dinilaatibigiwaji ica modaaЙЎМ¶igotibeci.
\q1 
\v 10 Jemaa me micataЙЎМ¶a deЙЎМ¶etoinadi amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ayatetibigiwaji,
\q1 codaa micataЙЎМ¶a diЙЎМ¶idioka limedi moyoyaЙЎМ¶aditedibece niЙЎМ¶inoa ane dakaketema.вҖқ
\p 
\v 11 Enice, jigika, вҖңInoa judeutedi, domigidioka limedi moyototedice AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane dixipe oditaЙЎМ¶a jiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶ite ane lanikadi?вҖқ AЙЎМ¶idioka limedi moyototedice AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote lewiЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo judeutedi moniteloco nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a me doЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶aditeda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, eotedibige monocetema niЙЎМ¶ijoa ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi.
\v 12 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eliodi me ibinie eledi noiigitigi niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o leeЙЎМ¶odi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco loiigi me doЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶aditeda. Codaa eliodi me ibinie niЙЎМ¶ijo ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi, leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo ane judeutedi moniaditema niliicaЙЎМ¶ajetedi anewi. NiЙЎМ¶ina nigodopitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijoa judeutedi aneniditediogi, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji daЙЎМ¶axatace me ibinie niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi.
\s1 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote lewiЙЎМ¶a ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi
\p 
\v 13 Natigide ejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji ane daЙЎМ¶akaami judeutedi. JowooЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me idimonyatediogi ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi. JowooЙЎМ¶odi me ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi niЙЎМ¶ida ibakedi ane najigotediwa.
\v 14 IjoatokaaЙЎМ¶a jakadi me jao niЙЎМ¶ijo emaЙЎМ¶a yoiigi monocetaЙЎМ¶adomitiwaji, amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a icawaanigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aneote lewiЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ida ibakedi.
\v 15 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko digoina iiЙЎМ¶o ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi odopitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo ane judeutedi me dowocetetege. NiЙЎМ¶ina nige dibatacetege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ijoa judeutedi, odaa eo meliodi ЙЎМ¶odinikegi leeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote me newiЙЎМ¶atace niЙЎМ¶ijoa judeutedi.
\p 
\v 16 Nigoyajigotalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji paon liwai, odaa iditawece paon eledi nebi. (Jotigide laamipi judeutedi liciagi niЙЎМ¶ijo paon liwai. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji dibatetege, odaa eledi dibatetege lionigipi). Nigoyajigotalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji litodi naЙЎМ¶ana niale, libiwedi eletidi nepilidi.
\v 17 Inoatecibece libiwedi nawodigije oliveira onakagidi. Odaa libiwe oliveira loidena joЙЎМ¶oyexocaЙЎМ¶aditege naЙЎМ¶ajo ane dinoke libiwe naЙЎМ¶ajo eledi oliveira. Odaa naЙЎМ¶ajo gela libiwe ja ili, codaa me dione, leeЙЎМ¶odi litodi. NiЙЎМ¶inoa judeutedi liciagi naЙЎМ¶ajo nawodigije oliveira. AkamaЙЎМ¶akaamitiwaji ane daЙЎМ¶akaamiteda judeutedi baЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adiciagi naЙЎМ¶ajo libiwe anoka oyexocaЙЎМ¶aditeloco eledi. Natigide abaategetiwaji loniciwaЙЎМ¶a codaa me lewiЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yajigotediogi loiigi judeutedi.
\v 18 AЙЎМ¶ele diЙЎМ¶ikaniticoace, daaditaЙЎМ¶adiaaЙЎМ¶ica mawiite ijoa judeutedi ane liciaco libiwedi oliveira ane dinoke. Ayakadi daЙЎМ¶adinaЙЎМ¶axakenitibecetiwaji, igaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ida makaami ЙЎМ¶adiciagi micoataЙЎМ¶a libiwedi niale. NaЙЎМ¶ana libiwe niale adowediteloco litodi, pida litodi yajigota liweenigi niЙЎМ¶inoa libiwedi.
\p 
\v 19 Pida ane daЙЎМ¶akaami judeutedi menitiwaji, вҖңOnakagidi niЙЎМ¶ijoa libiwedi owotibige moyexocaЙЎМ¶aditini eledi libiwe. Odaa ЙЎМ¶odiciagi naЙЎМ¶ajo eledi libiwe.вҖқ
\v 20 Ewi monakagidi niЙЎМ¶ijoa libiwedi anoiciaceeketege judeutedi. Pida niЙЎМ¶ijoa judeutedi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶eetediogi me loiigi leeЙЎМ¶odi aЙЎМ¶onakato, odaa akaamitiwaji etiЙЎМ¶adawanaЙЎМ¶atitege loiigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji leeЙЎМ¶odi manakatoni. Odaa jinaЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a adinaЙЎМ¶axakenitibecetiwaji, pida adinoweti.
\v 21 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja iloikatidi judeutedi, anoiciaceeketege niЙЎМ¶ijoa niale libiwedi anoyakagidi. Odaa akaamitiwaji nigikani manakatoni, akaami eleditetiwaji ЙЎМ¶adiloikatiti.
\p 
\v 22 Ja jinataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ica AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meliodi meletetema oko, codaa iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a me iloikatidi niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko. Iloikatidi niЙЎМ¶ina anoika monakato, pida eliodi meletedaЙЎМ¶adomitiwaji nige diЙЎМ¶ikaniteda manakatoni. Nigikanitiwaji manakatoni, odaa aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶eetedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji makaami loiigi, ЙЎМ¶adiciagi niЙЎМ¶ijoa libiwedi oliveira anonakagidi.
\v 23 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa judeutedi, nigodopitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji monakatotace, odaa ja yawanaЙЎМ¶aditacetege loiigi, igaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yakadi meote modopitacalo.
\v 24 Odaa akaamitiwaji ane daЙЎМ¶akaami judeutedi, ЙЎМ¶adiciagi naЙЎМ¶ajo libiwe oliveira loidena anoyakagidi, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyexocaЙЎМ¶aditeloco naЙЎМ¶ajo niale nawodigije, naЙЎМ¶ajo ane daЙЎМ¶a libiwe. Pida niЙЎМ¶ijoa judeutedi liciaco niЙЎМ¶ijoa anepaa libiwedi naЙЎМ¶ajo niale nawodigije anonakagidi. Adakake doЙЎМ¶oyexocaЙЎМ¶aditacedini libiwedi anoyakagidi naЙЎМ¶ajo niale oliveira loidena. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee aЙЎМ¶ica laЙЎМ¶aliigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji daЙЎМ¶a yexocaЙЎМ¶aditacedini niЙЎМ¶ijoa libiwedi anida aneetege naЙЎМ¶ajo niale nawodigije, odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee me yawanaЙЎМ¶aditacetege judeutedi niЙЎМ¶ijo loiigi.
\s1 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji iwikode inatawece oko
\p 
\v 25 Inioxoadipi. Jemaa mowooЙЎМ¶oti ane neloЙЎМ¶oditedoЙЎМ¶owa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, amanagawini aЙЎМ¶adinaЙЎМ¶axakenitibecetiwaji leeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aneote mowooЙЎМ¶oti. NikeetedoЙЎМ¶owa midi niЙЎМ¶ina noiigi judeutedi dakake laaleЙЎМ¶ena nigepaaЙЎМ¶icota monotalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji inatawece niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi aneniditediogi.
\v 26 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote lewiЙЎМ¶a inatawece loiigi Israel. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a yalaЙЎМ¶ata niЙЎМ¶ida niciagi, niЙЎМ¶ijo mee,
\q1 вҖңЗӨanewikatitoЙЎМ¶odi icoЙЎМ¶oticogi manitaЙЎМ¶a nigotaЙЎМ¶a SiГЈo,
\q1 odaa enagi napitaЙЎМ¶adi inoatawece libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco oko anida aneetege licoЙЎМ¶egi JacГі.
\q1 
\v 27 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji mee,
\q1 вҖҳJao micota ane igegitiogi,
\q1 inapitaЙЎМ¶adi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco anida aneetege licoЙЎМ¶egi JacГі.вҖҷвҖқ
\p 
\v 28 Judeutedi aЙЎМ¶odibatege nibodicetedi anele ane icoЙЎМ¶otedigi miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi me laxakawepodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eotedibige me yakadi me ЙЎМ¶adibinienitetiwaji ane daЙЎМ¶akaami judeutedi. Pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ixipetedice noiigi Israel, codaa yemaa leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo ane ligegitetege laamipi.
\v 29 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iolatedicoace oko, codaa niЙЎМ¶ina me ibinie, aiigi ane lowooko.
\v 30 NiЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide akaamitiwaji ane daЙЎМ¶akaami judeutedi aЙЎМ¶iwaЙЎМ¶ati AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Pida natigide AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЙЎМ¶adiwikodenitetiwaji leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijoa judeutedi me doЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶aditeda.
\v 31 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee natigide niЙЎМ¶ijoa judeutedi aЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji leeЙЎМ¶odi me ЙЎМ¶adiwikodenitetiwaji. Eotedibige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yakadi me niwikodetediniwace.
\v 32 LeeЙЎМ¶odi ijotawece oko aЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa jeЙЎМ¶eote me diЙЎМ¶icata ane yakadi me ika nibeyacaЙЎМ¶a, micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a dinigoetiniwace, daЙЎМ¶a niwilogojegipi. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eotedibige me niwikodetediniwace inatawece oko.
\s1 Leeditibige me joЙЎМ¶eeЙЎМ¶atalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji
\p 
\v 33 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yowooЙЎМ¶odi inoatawece, codaa yowooЙЎМ¶odi oninitecibeci ane loenataka. AЙЎМ¶ica liciagi. AjakataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a jowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶icoa ane lowooko, codaa ajakataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a jowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a inoatawece niЙЎМ¶icoa aneote.
\v 34 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eeta AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a, anee,
\q1 вҖңAmiijo ane yakadi me yowooЙЎМ¶odi icoa lowooko ЗӨoniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji?
\q1 Codaa amiijo ane yakadi me iladee?
\q1 
\v 35 Codaa amiijo baanaЙЎМ¶a ica anigini ane yajigotalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji,
\q1 odaa ja nibeotege loojedi?вҖқ
\m 
\v 36 IgaataЙЎМ¶a iliidaЙЎМ¶adi inoatawece, codaa inoatawece aninoa idioka limedi minoa leeЙЎМ¶odi nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi, codaa inoatawece aninoa, iniaa loenataka, codaa modoЙЎМ¶etetalo leeЙЎМ¶odi loenataka. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi me leeditibige midioka limedi me joЙЎМ¶eeЙЎМ¶atalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee. (AmГ©m).
\c 12
\s1 ЗӨodewiЙЎМ¶a me jibaaЙЎМ¶atema AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji
\p 
\v 1 Enice inioxoadipi, jipokotaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji mewi madinajicitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, leeЙЎМ¶odi eliodi me ЙЎМ¶odiwikode. NiЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide oyalegi eijedi moibootalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji mowotibige me ninitedibece, pida oko baЙЎМ¶a idiniboonaЙЎМ¶atalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЙЎМ¶odiciagi niЙЎМ¶ina niboonigi ewikegi. Odaa iniokiniwateda me ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶atema. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa ane yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Odaa joaniЙЎМ¶idaa aneo mewi me joЙЎМ¶eeЙЎМ¶atalo.
\v 2 JinaЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a iwitece lakataЙЎМ¶a okotigi niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o anodakapetege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Pida ikani AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iigi ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali, amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji ane yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Ane yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eletaЙЎМ¶adomi, aЙЎМ¶icaadaЙЎМ¶a beyagitaЙЎМ¶adomi, codaa me ninikatidi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶adomi.
\p 
\v 3 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji najigotediwa ibakedi, codaa aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a najigotediwa yoniciwaЙЎМ¶a me jao niЙЎМ¶ida ibakedi. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi mejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji, jinaЙЎМ¶aleetibige daЙЎМ¶akaami ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egipi, igaataЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶akaami ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egipitetiwaji. Pida nigakamaЙЎМ¶a adinowootiwaji, owoo niЙЎМ¶ica anele, ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, codaa jinoЙЎМ¶owootiwaji doЙЎМ¶oleetibige me ЙЎМ¶adeloki. AkamaЙЎМ¶akaami leeditibige madiniwini amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a anati naЙЎМ¶a yajigotedaЙЎМ¶awa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЙЎМ¶atiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi.
\v 4 Digowoo niЙЎМ¶ina ЙЎМ¶odolaadi owidi liwailidi, pida idiokidi ЙЎМ¶odolaadi aneiteloco. Codaa oniditeci liwai ida ane libakedi.
\v 5 NiЙЎМ¶ida moko, oko eliodi, ЙЎМ¶odiciagi liwailidi ЙЎМ¶odolaadi. Pida okomoЙЎМ¶okotiwage ЙЎМ¶odiciagi ЙЎМ¶odolaadi mokiditece. Codaa niЙЎМ¶ida moko okotawece ЙЎМ¶odexogotege Cristo. Odaa okotawece ida anejinaЙЎМ¶atiwage digo minoataЙЎМ¶a liwailidi ЙЎМ¶odolaadi.
\v 6 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa me daЙЎМ¶a diniciamico ЙЎМ¶odixaketedi ane najigotedoЙЎМ¶owa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me jibakenaЙЎМ¶a. Nigida ЙЎМ¶odixakedi mejinaЙЎМ¶atiogi niЙЎМ¶ina anonakato ЗӨoniotagodi niЙЎМ¶ica ane yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ligegitediogi, jaoЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ida ЙЎМ¶obakedi me jinakatonaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 7 Nige najigotedoЙЎМ¶owa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЙЎМ¶odixakedi me jaxawanaЙЎМ¶a eledi oko, dice jaxawanaЙЎМ¶a. Nige najigotedoЙЎМ¶owa ЙЎМ¶odixakedi me jiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶atece lotaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, dice jiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 8 Nige najigotedoЙЎМ¶owa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЙЎМ¶odixakedi me jaoЙЎМ¶a loniciwaЙЎМ¶a eledi oko modiotece Cristo, dice jaoЙЎМ¶o loniciwaЙЎМ¶a. Nige najigotedoЙЎМ¶owa ЙЎМ¶onimaweneЙЎМ¶egi me jedianaЙЎМ¶atece oko anigidi ane yopotibige, dice jedianaЙЎМ¶a, mele ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena. Nige najigotedoЙЎМ¶owa ЙЎМ¶odixakedi me jiiЙЎМ¶enatakanaЙЎМ¶a, dice jibakenaЙЎМ¶a minitawece ЙЎМ¶odoniciwaЙЎМ¶a me jiiЙЎМ¶enatakanaЙЎМ¶a. Nige najigotedoЙЎМ¶owa ЙЎМ¶odixakedi me jiwikodenaЙЎМ¶a eledi oko, dice ЙЎМ¶odinitibece me jiwikodenaЙЎМ¶a.
\p 
\v 9 Emaani eledi oko manitawece ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶ena. Codaa oxaxini ane beyagi, pida oleetibige me iwitece anele.
\v 10 Oleetibige meliodi memaani niЙЎМ¶ina anonakato ЗӨoniotagodi micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adoiigiwepodi. Oleetibige maweniЙЎМ¶ideni eledi oko.
\v 11 JinaЙЎМ¶akaami abaciЙЎМ¶egitema ЙЎМ¶abakedi. Awii libakedi ЗӨoniotagodi manitawece codaa mele ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶ena.
\v 12 Aniniitibeci leeЙЎМ¶odi manibeoonitibigege lanokegi ЗӨoniotagodi. Adinatiitalo ЙЎМ¶adawikodico, codaa jiniЙЎМ¶ikani motaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 13 Edianitecetiwaji ЙЎМ¶anioxoadipi ganigidi laЙЎМ¶alanigi ane yopotibige. Codaa abaatege oko ane yopotibige limedi.
\p 
\v 14 Ipokitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ibinie niЙЎМ¶ina ane igaalatibigaЙЎМ¶aji. Ipokitalo me ibinie, pida jiniЙЎМ¶ipokitalo deЙЎМ¶eote ane beyagitema.
\v 15 Oleetibige me ЙЎМ¶adinikaЙЎМ¶awa ane ninitibece. Codaa anoeni nigini ane anoe.
\v 16 Aniwotitema eledi oko. JinaЙЎМ¶akaami anaЙЎМ¶axakeneЙЎМ¶egi, pida oleetibige me ЙЎМ¶adokaaЙЎМ¶edi ane daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi. JinaЙЎМ¶aleetibige daЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶axa mida ЙЎМ¶adixakedi caticedi niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko.
\p 
\v 17 Nigica aneo ane beyagitaЙЎМ¶adomi, jinaЙЎМ¶awii ane beyagitema. Oleetibige mawii anoyakadi eledi oko mele.
\v 18 Nigakatitiwaji, awii me ЙЎМ¶adilakiitege inatawece oko.
\v 19 Inioxoadipi yemaanigipi. JinoЙЎМ¶oleetibige daЙЎМ¶a oojetee. Pida ikanitece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji mepaa yelatetema, odaa eote lawikodico niЙЎМ¶ini oko aneo ane beyagitaЙЎМ¶adomitiwaji. IgaataЙЎМ¶a maditaЙЎМ¶a lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji mee ЗӨoniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, вҖңEmokee mida yoniciwaЙЎМ¶a me joojete. Odaa jao lawikodico niЙЎМ¶ina oko anowo ane beyagitaЙЎМ¶adomitiwaji.вҖқ
\v 20 Dice awii aneeta lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, niЙЎМ¶ijo neЙЎМ¶ee, вҖңNige nigicile ЙЎМ¶adaxakawa, edianitece niweenigi, nige yeloadi ecibi, acipeЙЎМ¶eni. Igaanigawii niЙЎМ¶ida aneni, odaa eliodi me niboliЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adaxakawa.вҖқ
\v 21 JiniЙЎМ¶ikani ane beyagi daЙЎМ¶a dinigaanyetaЙЎМ¶adici. Pida aЙЎМ¶ekeni ane beyagi mawii anele.
\c 13
\s1 Leeditibige mejiwaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶a anida naЙЎМ¶atetigi
\p 
\v 1 Leeditibige mokotawece ejiwaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶a inatawece anida naЙЎМ¶atetigi. IgaataЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶ica ini ane diiЙЎМ¶enataka ane daЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yajigote naЙЎМ¶atetigi, pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji inaaЙЎМ¶eyate niЙЎМ¶inoa anida naЙЎМ¶atetigi digoina iiЙЎМ¶o.
\v 2 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane lakapetegi niЙЎМ¶ina anida naЙЎМ¶atetigi digoina iiЙЎМ¶o, aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a lakapetegi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina lakapetegi niЙЎМ¶ina ane niiЙЎМ¶enatakanaЙЎМ¶a nigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi nawikodeeЙЎМ¶a, iloikatidi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 3 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina anowo anele aЙЎМ¶odoita niЙЎМ¶ina anida naЙЎМ¶atetigi. Pida inokina niЙЎМ¶ina anowo ane beyagi, boЙЎМ¶odoita niЙЎМ¶ina anida naЙЎМ¶atetigi. Akaami nige deЙЎМ¶emaani madoii anida naЙЎМ¶atetigi, dice oleetibige mawii anele, odaa ele moyalaЙЎМ¶atibigaЙЎМ¶aji.
\v 4 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina ane diiЙЎМ¶enataka digoina iiЙЎМ¶o eo libakedi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, nibakedi aneletaЙЎМ¶adomi. Pida nigawii ane beyagi, enice ele madoii. IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina ane diiЙЎМ¶enataka ewi mida loniciwaЙЎМ¶a me diiЙЎМ¶enatakataЙЎМ¶awa metiЙЎМ¶adiloikatiti. LeeЙЎМ¶odi eo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji libakedi, odaa iloikatidi niЙЎМ¶ina oko aneo ane beyagi, igaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja yelatetema libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco niЙЎМ¶ina oko.
\v 5 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi me leeditibige me iwaЙЎМ¶ati niЙЎМ¶inoa anida naЙЎМ¶atetigi, aleeЙЎМ¶odi madoiita mawikodee, pida leeЙЎМ¶odi me eemiteetece catiwedi ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶ena niЙЎМ¶ina mawii ane beyagi, oЙЎМ¶oa, domige ina anele.
\p 
\v 6 Codaa joaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi leeditibige medianitiwaji inionigi-eliodi mepaaЙЎМ¶odibatege ЙЎМ¶aninyeelo niЙЎМ¶inoa anida naЙЎМ¶atetigi, igaataЙЎМ¶a owo libakedi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yajigotediogi.
\v 7 Enice ediani ane ЙЎМ¶anaalewetema inionigi-eliodi, codaa me okanicodaaЙЎМ¶icoa eletidi ЙЎМ¶anaalewe. Eemiteetibige codaa maweniЙЎМ¶idenitiwaji inatawece anida naЙЎМ¶atetigi.
\s1 Ica ane leeditibige miniЙЎМ¶ata eledi oko
\p 
\v 8 JiniЙЎМ¶ikani diЙЎМ¶idioka limedi midiwa ЙЎМ¶anaalewe. Pida leeditibige midioka limedi memaani eledi oko. IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina ane yemaa eledi oko, jeЙЎМ¶eote icoatawece niЙЎМ¶icoa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji anetiЙЎМ¶odiiЙЎМ¶eta me jaoЙЎМ¶a.
\v 9 Mee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, вҖңEmaani eledi oko digo aneni madinemaani.вҖқ NiЙЎМ¶ina oko nigeo niЙЎМ¶ida niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi, odaa jeЙЎМ¶eote niЙЎМ¶ijoa eletidi liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane iditedini MoisГ©s, вҖңJinaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adoomatewa ane daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adodawa. JinaЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a aijee. JinoЙЎМ¶olice. JinaЙЎМ¶a aniliitibige eledi oko. JineЙЎМ¶emaani niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶anebi.вҖқ Odaa niЙЎМ¶idiwa niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco codaa okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica eledi liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liciagi niЙЎМ¶ijo niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi anee, вҖңLajo memaani eledi oko digo aneni madinemaani.вҖқ
\v 10 NiЙЎМ¶ina ane yemaa eledi oko inokeo aneletema. Odaa joaniЙЎМ¶idaa niЙЎМ¶ina ane yemaa eledi oko jeЙЎМ¶eote icoatawece niЙЎМ¶icoa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\p 
\v 11 NiЙЎМ¶ica noko lanokegi Cristo me dopitedijo me ЙЎМ¶odewikatidi jeЙЎМ¶epaanaЙЎМ¶a nipegi, aЙЎМ¶alee liciagi niЙЎМ¶ijo noko maleekoka jinakatonaЙЎМ¶a ЗӨoniotagodi. Enice, joЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji me leeditibige madinoweti, codaa madinemaanitiwage.
\v 12 Liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina enoale naЙЎМ¶a ixomaЙЎМ¶atice, odaa ja yeloЙЎМ¶otibige, Codaa leeditibige me jikanaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶inoa ane beyagi aneo niЙЎМ¶ina oko anida aneetege nexocaЙЎМ¶a. Leeditibige me ЙЎМ¶odigotema me jaoЙЎМ¶ate nibaketedi anele manitaЙЎМ¶a lokokena.
\v 13 JaoЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a liciagi niЙЎМ¶idi oko ane newiЙЎМ¶a manitaЙЎМ¶a lokokena. JinaЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a jacapenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶atibece migetaЙЎМ¶a jacipaЙЎМ¶atibece; codaa jinaЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a jitineЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶ododawadipi; codaa jinaЙЎМ¶a jidelaЙЎМ¶a oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a jelokojoЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 14 BiЙЎМ¶ida leeditibige me ЙЎМ¶adigomi mawii inokina anele, igaataЙЎМ¶a ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus Cristo yajigotedaЙЎМ¶awa loniciwaЙЎМ¶a mawii anele. JinaЙЎМ¶a domoЙЎМ¶owoo mawii ane beyagi, anokomaЙЎМ¶a jilidaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶atibige me jaoЙЎМ¶a.
\c 14
\s1 JinaЙЎМ¶a alomeЙЎМ¶eni ЙЎМ¶anioxoa
\p 
\v 1 Abaatege ЙЎМ¶adiwigotigitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina ane deЙЎМ¶eliodi eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi. Pida jinaЙЎМ¶abaatege daЙЎМ¶adinotigimadenitege leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶icoa anaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a lowooko.
\v 2 Inatecibece oko oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi moyakadi moyeligo okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica niweenigi. Pida inatecibece eledi oko ane deЙЎМ¶eliodi eliwaЙЎМ¶atakanaЙЎМ¶a, oyeligo inokinoa niЙЎМ¶inoa ane ЙЎМ¶otanigijedi.
\v 3 NiЙЎМ¶ina ane yeligo okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica niweenigi, leeditibige me daЙЎМ¶a iЙЎМ¶oadita niЙЎМ¶ina aninoka yeligo ane ЙЎМ¶otanigijedi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a yeligo libole, leeditibige me deЙЎМ¶ee me libatiigi niЙЎМ¶ina eledi me yeligo okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica niweenigi. IgaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja dibatetege niЙЎМ¶ini oko.
\v 4 NiЙЎМ¶ida makaami aЙЎМ¶ica ЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶atetigi malomeЙЎМ¶eni liotagi eledi oko. NiЙЎМ¶ina niotagi, nigeo nibakedi anele, oЙЎМ¶oa, domigeo nibakedi ane beyagi, niotagodi jiЙЎМ¶iniaa iwi libakedi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liotagi eo niЙЎМ¶ina anele, igaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yajigote nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi meo nibakedi anele.
\p 
\v 5 Inatecibece odiletibige diЙЎМ¶ida noko ane eneЙЎМ¶egi ida ane jaoЙЎМ¶a, aliciagi niЙЎМ¶inoa eletidi nokododi. Pida inatecibece oko jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶odiletibige diЙЎМ¶inoatawece nokododi diniciamico. Oninitecibeci leeditibige mewi me dowooko amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica aneletema.
\v 6 NiЙЎМ¶ina ane diletibige diЙЎМ¶ida noko me daЙЎМ¶axa mida ane jaoЙЎМ¶a, yotete niЙЎМ¶ida noko me doЙЎМ¶etetalo ЗӨoniotagodi. Codaa niЙЎМ¶ina ane yeligo okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica niweenigi, niЙЎМ¶ina naЙЎМ¶a yeligo, doЙЎМ¶etetalo ЗӨoniotagodi, codaa diniotagodetalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji leeЙЎМ¶odi midi ane yeligo. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina ane inoka yeligo ane ЙЎМ¶otanigijedi, aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a doЙЎМ¶etetalo ЗӨoniotagodi leeЙЎМ¶odi me diniotagodetalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji midi ane yeligo.
\v 7 AЙЎМ¶ica ini anini ЙЎМ¶odiwigotigi ane yakadi mee, вҖңAbeyagitema eledi oko me idewiЙЎМ¶a, oЙЎМ¶oa mige ideleo.вҖқ
\v 8 Nige ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶a, ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶atema ЗӨoniotagodi. Nige ЙЎМ¶odeleo, ЙЎМ¶odeleotema ЗӨoniotagodi. Enice nige ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶a, oЙЎМ¶oa, domige ЙЎМ¶odeleo, idioka limedi moko nebi ЗӨoniotagodi.
\v 9 IgaataЙЎМ¶a Cristo yeleo, pida yewiЙЎМ¶atace eotedibige me Niotagodi Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a codaa moko anepaЙЎМ¶alee ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶a.
\p 
\v 10 Enice igaamee ina meni ЙЎМ¶anioxoa me dibatГЎ? Codaa igame leeЙЎМ¶odi me daЙЎМ¶adiaaЙЎМ¶ica mawii ЙЎМ¶anioxoa? IgaataЙЎМ¶a icota noko mokotawece idinikeenaЙЎМ¶a lodoe Cristo. Odaa Cristo ja najigotedoЙЎМ¶owa niЙЎМ¶ica ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a me jibaЙЎМ¶atege me ЙЎМ¶onoЙЎМ¶eedi leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶odoenatakatema.
\v 11 IgaataЙЎМ¶a diniditeloco lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji,
\q1 вҖңMee ЗӨoniotagodi,
\q1 вҖҳIdewiЙЎМ¶a, odaa jinaЙЎМ¶awienatakani minatawece oko oyamaЙЎМ¶atedi lokotidi yodoe,
\q1 codaa inatawece oko moditiwa me Ee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.вҖҷвҖқ
\m 
\v 12 Odaa joaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee, okotawece jeloЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶atalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji icoatawece niЙЎМ¶icoa ane ЙЎМ¶odoenataka.
\s1 JinaЙЎМ¶awii ЙЎМ¶anioxoa meyamaЙЎМ¶atice eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi
\p 
\v 13 Enice jikanaЙЎМ¶a me idinalomeЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a. Leeditibige mowoo me daЙЎМ¶adiaaЙЎМ¶awii ЙЎМ¶anioxoa meyamaЙЎМ¶atice eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi, migetaЙЎМ¶a ika me diotece ЗӨoniotagodi.
\v 14 LeeЙЎМ¶odi me ee nebi Cristo, odaa jowooЙЎМ¶odi codaa ajawienataka me diЙЎМ¶ica niweenigi ane daЙЎМ¶a yakadi me jelicaЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi moibootiogi niwicidi. Pida nigica ane diletibige diЙЎМ¶ica niweenigi ane daЙЎМ¶a yakadi me jelicaЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi moibootiogi niwicidi, nige yeligo niЙЎМ¶ica niweenigi, odaa ja dibatГЎ.
\v 15 Nigawii ЙЎМ¶anioxoa magecaЙЎМ¶alo leeЙЎМ¶odi niweenigi anelici, jiЙЎМ¶ikeeni me deЙЎМ¶emaani ЙЎМ¶anioxoa. Pida Cristo ja yeleotetema niЙЎМ¶ini ЙЎМ¶anioxoa. Enice jinaЙЎМ¶awii me ika metiwaЙЎМ¶ataka leeЙЎМ¶odi niweenigi anelici.
\v 16 JinaЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶awii eledi oko modotaЙЎМ¶atibige niЙЎМ¶ica anakati mele.
\v 17 IgaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji iiЙЎМ¶e catiwedi ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶enali. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi aleeditibige daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odigecaЙЎМ¶aleЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ica ane jelicaЙЎМ¶a, migetaЙЎМ¶a ane jacipaЙЎМ¶a. Pida leeditibige minoka jaoЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, codaa joleeЙЎМ¶atibige minatawece oko ilaЙЎМ¶atiwage, codaa midokida ЙЎМ¶odowoogo inaa ЙЎМ¶odinikegi. JakataЙЎМ¶a me jaoЙЎМ¶ate inoatawece leeЙЎМ¶odi loniciwaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo.
\v 18 Nige niЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee niЙЎМ¶ina liotagi Cristo, odaa yocaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa eo me ninitedibece. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko odeemitetibige niЙЎМ¶ina liotagi Cristo.
\p 
\v 19 Enice joleeЙЎМ¶atibige niЙЎМ¶ica aneo me ЙЎМ¶odilaЙЎМ¶atiwage, codaa joleeЙЎМ¶atibige me jaoЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina ane yaxawa eledi oko me ilitema eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi.
\v 20 JinaЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a aaЙЎМ¶ati niЙЎМ¶ica AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aneotetema ЙЎМ¶anioxoa leeЙЎМ¶odi niweenigi anelici. Yakadi melici okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica niweenigi, pida jinaЙЎМ¶a domeЙЎМ¶elici niЙЎМ¶ica niweenigi aneo eledi oko me eyamaЙЎМ¶atice eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi.
\v 21 Ele nige deЙЎМ¶elici libole, nige daЙЎМ¶a acipe viinyo, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a awii anigetiЙЎМ¶ini aneo ЙЎМ¶anioxoa me dibatГЎ, oditaЙЎМ¶a eyamaЙЎМ¶atice eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi.
\p 
\v 22 Nigica ananatitece meo niЙЎМ¶ida niciagi, oteteni makamokakaami mowooЙЎМ¶oti iniaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. NiЙЎМ¶ina oko ninitibece, niЙЎМ¶ina me daЙЎМ¶a deemitetece catiwedi laaleЙЎМ¶ena me dibatГЎ leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ina loenatagi aneo.
\v 23 Pida niЙЎМ¶ina ane dinawietibece, ane diletibige daЙЎМ¶a dibatГЎ niЙЎМ¶ina me yeligo libole, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji iloikatidi niЙЎМ¶ina oko leeЙЎМ¶odi aЙЎМ¶eo niЙЎМ¶ica ane deemitetece laaleЙЎМ¶ena. IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane diletibige me daЙЎМ¶a ilaЙЎМ¶atice meo anigidi, pida eo, odaa ja dibatГЎ (igaataЙЎМ¶a adioteci ane yowooЙЎМ¶odi me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a).
\c 15
\s1 Leeditibige me jocaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atibigo eledi oko
\p 
\v 1 NiЙЎМ¶ida moko baanaЙЎМ¶a yoniciwadi ЙЎМ¶otiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi leeditibige me idinatiiЙЎМ¶atalo niЙЎМ¶inoa loenataka niЙЎМ¶ina analee deЙЎМ¶eliodi eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi, codaa idinatiiЙЎМ¶atalo niЙЎМ¶inoa lowooko, icaaЙЎМ¶ica nige daЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odiwoditema lowooko. AЙЎМ¶ele daЙЎМ¶a jaoЙЎМ¶a inokina anokomoka aneletoЙЎМ¶odomi.
\v 2 Pida oninitecibeci leeditibige me yocaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶etibigo nioxoa, meo niЙЎМ¶ica aneletema, eotibige me yaxawa me ili eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi.
\v 3 IgaataЙЎМ¶a Cristo jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee aЙЎМ¶eote ini anepaЙЎМ¶a yemaa. Dinatite niЙЎМ¶ijoa lawikodico, digo aneeta me diniditeloco lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. NiЙЎМ¶ica Cristo naЙЎМ¶a yotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e Eliodi, meeteta,
\q1 вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ijo anoyametibigaЙЎМ¶aji,
\q1 aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a etidame.вҖқ
\m 
\v 4 IgaataЙЎМ¶a ijoatawece ane diniditeloco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi, niЙЎМ¶ica jotigide, ijoatawece diniditedini metiЙЎМ¶odiiЙЎМ¶axi me idinatiiЙЎМ¶atalo ЙЎМ¶odawikodico, codaa mowo mabo ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi me inibeoonaЙЎМ¶atibigege lanokegi Cristo.
\p 
\v 5 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji najigotedoЙЎМ¶owa ЙЎМ¶odoniciwaЙЎМ¶a me jakataЙЎМ¶a me idinatiiЙЎМ¶atalo ЙЎМ¶odawikodico, codaa meote mabo ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena. Odaa jipokotalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ЙЎМ¶adaxawanitetiwaji midokida ane ЙЎМ¶adowoogo, codaa midioka limedi me ЙЎМ¶adilakiitiwagetiwaji, digo anee Jesus Cristo me nikeetedoЙЎМ¶owa.
\v 6 JiЙЎМ¶idaa ane jipokotalo amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a akaamitawece ateciЙЎМ¶i, micataЙЎМ¶a doЙЎМ¶okinitece oko, odaa akaamitawecetiwaji oЙЎМ¶eetetalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, ane Eliodi ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus Cristo.
\s1 NiЙЎМ¶inoa nibodicetedi anele aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶icotiogi ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi
\p 
\v 7 Dicabaategetiwaji eledi oko, digo anigotedoЙЎМ¶owa Cristo me dibatedoЙЎМ¶ogi, amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a odoЙЎМ¶etetibigimece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ina oko.
\v 8 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji joaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi Cristo me dinajigo me liotagi judeutedi, eotedibige me ikee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me daЙЎМ¶a ixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice ane ligegi, pida eote ane ligegitediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide laamipi judeutedi.
\v 9 Codaa dinajigo me liotagi judeutedi eotedibige niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi modoЙЎМ¶etetalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, leeЙЎМ¶odi me iwikodetediogi. Davi yalaЙЎМ¶ata niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi maditaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi, niЙЎМ¶ijo mee,
\q1 вҖңJoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi joЙЎМ¶etetaЙЎМ¶awa liwigotigi niЙЎМ¶idi ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi,
\q1 codaa jigaa enaco me joЙЎМ¶eteta ЗӨaboonaЙЎМ¶adi.вҖқ
\m 
\v 10 Eledi mee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a,
\q1 вҖңAkaamitiwaji ane daЙЎМ¶akaami judeutedi,
\q1 aniniitibecitiwaji,
\q1 awanitege niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane iomaЙЎМ¶aditedice!вҖқ
\m 
\v 11 Codaa eleditace mee,
\q1 вҖңAkaamitawecetiwaji ane daЙЎМ¶akaami judeutedi oЙЎМ¶eetetalo ЗӨoniotagodi!
\q1 IgaataЙЎМ¶a inatawece ane noiigi leeditibige modoЙЎМ¶etetalo.вҖқ
\m 
\v 12 Codaa me IsaГӯas iditeloco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi, niЙЎМ¶ijo mee,
\q1 вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ica anida aneetege licoЙЎМ¶egi JessГ© enagi me iiЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi.
\q1 Odaa onibeotege me yewikatiditibigiwaji.вҖқ
\m (NiЙЎМ¶ica JessГ©, Davi eliodi).
\p 
\v 13 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji jiЙЎМ¶iniaaЙЎМ¶eote me inibeoonaЙЎМ¶atege lanokegi ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus. Odaa jipokotalo meliodi me yajigotedaЙЎМ¶awa ЙЎМ¶adinikegitiwaji, codaa meote mele ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali malee iwaЙЎМ¶atitetiwaji, amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yajigotaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo ЙЎМ¶animaweneЙЎМ¶egi mepaanaЙЎМ¶a anibeoonitege lanokegi ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus.
\s1 Paulo libakedi me yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece nibodicetedi anele miditaЙЎМ¶a ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi
\p 
\v 14 Inioxoadipi, emeЙЎМ¶eeta eliodi me jowooЙЎМ¶odi, codaa ajawienataka meliodi makaamitiwaji eletetema eledi oko, codaa jowooЙЎМ¶odi mowooЙЎМ¶oti anodaa diitigi ЙЎМ¶otiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi, codaa mowooЙЎМ¶oti madinoxoki madinajacaЙЎМ¶atitiwaji.
\v 15 Pida, inioxoadipi, jiditini ane igegi amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a jao manalakitibige niЙЎМ¶inoa anejitece. Aidoi me jidi naЙЎМ¶adi notaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi, igaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji idiomaЙЎМ¶aditedice me jao ane libakedi.
\v 16 IdiomaЙЎМ¶aditedice me ee liotagi Jesus Cristo, codaa maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a jiba miditaЙЎМ¶a ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi. NiЙЎМ¶ina mejitece nibodicetedi anele anoditece Jesus, jiba micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina sacerdoti ane yajigo niboonigitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Jaotibige niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi meniwaЙЎМ¶atakanaЙЎМ¶a, odaa ja liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina niboonigitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane dibatetege, jiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi ane ixipeticoace AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo mepoka nepiliditeda.
\p 
\v 17 Enice jakadi me idinabaketibece leeЙЎМ¶odi ibakeditema AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, leeЙЎМ¶odi me idexogotege Cristo.
\v 18 IgaataЙЎМ¶a inoka jemaa mejitece niЙЎМ¶inoa Cristo ane loenataka me idibake. Najigotediwa yoniciwaЙЎМ¶a me jao niЙЎМ¶ida nibakedi, codaa me jao niЙЎМ¶ijo ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi monakato ЗӨoniotagodi. NiЙЎМ¶idi oko oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶owajipatalo yotaЙЎМ¶a, codaa noЙЎМ¶onadi anodaaЙЎМ¶ee yewiЙЎМ¶a.
\v 19 Eleditace oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶onadi niЙЎМ¶inoa ane ЙЎМ¶obinico anoikee loniciwaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa me niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶etedi. Odaa joЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji leeЙЎМ¶odi loniciwaЙЎМ¶a Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa ibakedi niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a idixomaЙЎМ¶ateloco nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m, codaa me niЙЎМ¶inoa nigotadi anodipegitege, codaa minoatawece nigotadi neЙЎМ¶epaa nipodigi IlГӯria. Inoatawece nigotadi anejigotece ejitece nibodicetedi anele anoditece Cristo.
\v 20 Idioka limedi me idinoniciwaЙЎМ¶adi mejitece nibodicetedi anele anoyalaЙЎМ¶atalo Cristo midiwataЙЎМ¶a nigotadi analee diЙЎМ¶ica mowajipata moyalaЙЎМ¶atalo Cristo. IgaataЙЎМ¶a adomaЙЎМ¶a jemaa me ibakadi baaniЙЎМ¶ijo me libakadi eledi oko, micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane daЙЎМ¶a yemaa me dabiteЙЎМ¶etini liЙЎМ¶eladi ditibigimedi lipodaЙЎМ¶aladi baaniЙЎМ¶ijo me liЙЎМ¶eladi eledi oko.
\v 21 IdalaЙЎМ¶atalo ЗӨoniotagodi digo aneeta lotaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, niЙЎМ¶ina mee,
\q1 вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ijo ane diЙЎМ¶ica mowajipata moditece anodaaЙЎМ¶eeteda ЗӨoniotagodi,
\q1 niЙЎМ¶idi oko onadi,
\q1 codaa moyowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica anodaaЙЎМ¶eeteda.вҖқ
\s1 Paulo akaa lowoogo migo dalita nigotaЙЎМ¶a Roma
\p 
\v 22 Elioditibece me domaЙЎМ¶a jemaa me idalitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji, pida anaЙЎМ¶a jakadi leeЙЎМ¶odi ibakedi me jeloЙЎМ¶oditibece nibodicetedi anele anoditece Cristo miditaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi ane diЙЎМ¶ica mowajipatalo.
\v 23 Pida natigide ja jigodi niЙЎМ¶ida ibakedi minoataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶inoa nipodaЙЎМ¶a. Codaa ja jotigide me domaЙЎМ¶a jemaa me idalitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji.
\v 24 Odaa nige iniwiajeticogi digoida niiЙЎМ¶o Espanha, odaa jemaa me idalitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji. Odaa ejime epenaitedi midiaaЙЎМ¶ejo makaamitaЙЎМ¶atiwaji, makaami inikaЙЎМ¶awepoditetiwaji, odaa nigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi jemaa madaxawanitiwaji me iniwiajeticogi nigepaa Espanha.
\v 25 Pida niЙЎМ¶ina natigide ejigo nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a jaxawa noiigi anida aneetege Cristo manitaЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶ani nigotaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 26 IgaataЙЎМ¶a loiigi Cristo digoida niiЙЎМ¶otedi MacedГҙnia aniaa GrГ©cia oyakadi mele monioda dinyeelo moiwakateetigi niЙЎМ¶ijo madewetedi loiigi Cristo manitaЙЎМ¶a nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m.
\v 27 Idiaa lowoogo monioda dinyeelo, codaa diitigi amina naalewe moyaxawa noiigi judeutedi. NiЙЎМ¶idi ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi anonakato ЗӨoniotagodi leeditibige moyaxawa judeutedi madewetedi anonakato ЗӨoniotagodi. IgaataЙЎМ¶a oyeloЙЎМ¶oditiogi niЙЎМ¶ijo ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi anodaaЙЎМ¶eeteda libinico AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yajigotediogi.
\v 28 NigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi nige jigodi niЙЎМ¶ida ibakedi me jajigotiogi inoatawece dinyeelo niЙЎМ¶idi madewetedi. Igaanige idigo, odaa ja iniwiajeticogi Espanha, odaa inaaЙЎМ¶ejigotece makaamitaЙЎМ¶a, idalitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji.
\v 29 JowooЙЎМ¶odi nigejotaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji me idalitaЙЎМ¶awa, eliodi me ninitibece yaaleЙЎМ¶ena, igaataЙЎМ¶a Cristo owidi laxawanaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egitedomi. Codaa nigejotaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji jemaa mejitece niЙЎМ¶ida anigotediwa.
\p 
\v 30 Inioxoadipi, jao ipoketegi leeЙЎМ¶odi ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus Cristo, codaa leeЙЎМ¶odi Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote me idinemaanaЙЎМ¶atiwage. JipokotaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji ina baЙЎМ¶a otaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, digo aneji me jotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a idaxawa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 31 OtaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, ipokitalo me idotetetema niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi JudГ©ia ane doЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶aditeda ЗӨoniotagodi, codaa ipokitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote niЙЎМ¶idi loiigi digoida nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m modibatege niЙЎМ¶ida ibakedi.
\v 32 Odaa joaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee, nige yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, ejotaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji me ninitibece yaaleЙЎМ¶ena, odaa joniciwaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶a oninitecibeci ЙЎМ¶onioxoa.
\v 33 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote mele ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶enali. Jipokotalo midioka limedi miniwa makaamitaЙЎМ¶atiwaji. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee. (AmГ©m.)
\c 16
\s1 Paulo yecoaditibige lokaaЙЎМ¶etedi manitaЙЎМ¶a nigotaЙЎМ¶a Roma
\p 
\v 1 Jemaa me jeleЙЎМ¶etaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji ЙЎМ¶oniwaalo Febe, ane libakadi miditaЙЎМ¶a lapo anonakato ЗӨoniotagodi manitaЙЎМ¶a nigotaЙЎМ¶a CencrГ©ia.
\v 2 Jemaa mabaategetiwaji ЙЎМ¶oniwaalo leeЙЎМ¶odi mida aneetege ЗӨoniotagodi anodaa leeditibige modigo niЙЎМ¶ina liomaЙЎМ¶atagipi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji modibatege ЙЎМ¶onioxoadipi. Axawanitece okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica ane yopotibige, igaataЙЎМ¶a jiЙЎМ¶ijo me yaxawa eliodi oko, codaa ee ijo maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a idaxawa.
\p 
\v 3 Jemaa me idecoaditibige Priscila ijaa ГҒquila, yokaaЙЎМ¶etedi me jibaaЙЎМ¶atema Jesus Cristo.
\v 4 Priscila ijaa ГҒquila ja nigomaЙЎМ¶a moyeleotomi. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi meliodi me iniotagodetiogi. Pida aЙЎМ¶emokee, pida ijoatawece niЙЎМ¶ijoa lapoli anonakato ЗӨoniotagodi ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi, eledi odiniotagodetiogi Priscila ijaa ГҒquila.
\v 5 Codaa aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a idecoaditibige niЙЎМ¶ijo lapo anonakato ЗӨoniotagodi ane latecaЙЎМ¶adi liЙЎМ¶eladi Priscila ijaa ГҒquila.
\p Idecoaditibige EpГӘneto aneliodi me jemaatibigo. JiЙЎМ¶ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo odoejegi oko aneyiwaЙЎМ¶adi Cristo nipodigi ГҒsia.
\v 6 Idecoaditibige Maria aneliodi me dibatoЙЎМ¶odomi.
\v 7 Idecoaditibige AndrГҙnico aniaa JГәnias anida aneetege yoiigi. Anijo me iniwilaЙЎМ¶awepodi. NiЙЎМ¶inoa eletidi liiЙЎМ¶exedi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eliodi modeemitetibige, akaaЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi Cristo aniЙЎМ¶icatibige daЙЎМ¶a ejiwaЙЎМ¶adi.
\p 
\v 8 Idecoaditibige AmplГӯato, yokaaЙЎМ¶edi ane jemaa leeЙЎМ¶odi mida anejinaЙЎМ¶atege ЗӨoniotagodi.
\v 9 Idecoaditibige Urbano eledi ЙЎМ¶odokaaЙЎМ¶edi me jibaaЙЎМ¶atema Cristo, codaa aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a idecoaditibige EstГЎquis eledi yemaanigi.
\v 10 Idecoaditibige Apeles baanaЙЎМ¶a ikee meliodi meyiwaЙЎМ¶adi Cristo. Idecoaditibige ane liЙЎМ¶eladi minitaЙЎМ¶a AristГіbulo.
\v 11 Idecoaditibige HerodiГЈo ane yoiigi, codaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyiwaЙЎМ¶adi ЗӨoniotagodi ane liЙЎМ¶eladi minitaЙЎМ¶a Narciso.
\p 
\v 12 Idecoaditibige Trifena aniaa Trifosa, niЙЎМ¶ijo iwaalepodi anowo ЗӨoniotagodi libakedi. Codaa aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a idecoaditibige naЙЎМ¶ajo eledi ЙЎМ¶odokaaЙЎМ¶ete ЙЎМ¶odemaana PГ©rside aneliodi me dibatema ЗӨoniotagodi.
\v 13 Idecoaditibige Rufo liomaЙЎМ¶atagi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a idecoaditibige naЙЎМ¶ajo eliodo ane idigotiwa micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a ee lionigi.
\v 14 Idecoaditibige AsГӯncrito, Flegonte, Hermes, PГЎtrobas, ijaa Hermas, codaa me iditawece ЙЎМ¶onioxoadipi anidiaaЙЎМ¶i miditaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 15 Idecoaditibige FilГіlogo, JГәlia, Nereu ajaa niwaalo, codaa Olimpas ijaa ijotawece ane liomaЙЎМ¶atagipi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane iditibige miditaЙЎМ¶a.
\p 
\v 16 Adinecoatitiwaji amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ikeeni madinemaanitiwage, awiitibige me ninitedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. NiЙЎМ¶ina eletidi lapoli anoyiwaЙЎМ¶adi Cristo oyecoaditibigaЙЎМ¶ajitiwaji.
\s1 Paulo iladee niЙЎМ¶ijo lapo anonakato ЗӨoniotagodi manitaЙЎМ¶a nigotaЙЎМ¶a Roma
\p 
\v 17 Inioxoadipi. JipokotaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji manidakitigi niЙЎМ¶ina anodoletibige mowo mawalaceticoace, codaa madinotigimadenitiwage. NiЙЎМ¶idi noiigi oibeyacaЙЎМ¶adi eledi oko eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi, codaa modakapetege niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco ЙЎМ¶otiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi, baanaЙЎМ¶a owooЙЎМ¶otitetiwaji. Awalacetege niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi, jinaЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶awanitege.
\v 18 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina anowo eledi oko maniaditema eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi aliotagipi Cristo, ane ЗӨoniotagodi. Pida odioteci niЙЎМ¶icoa anepaa lidaЙЎМ¶ataka lolaadi. Ele me notaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a codaa oiletibigo oko, owotibige moyakadi moinaale niЙЎМ¶ina ane diЙЎМ¶ica lixakedi.
\v 19 Pida inatawece oko oyowooЙЎМ¶odi me iwitecetiwaji ЗӨoniotagodi, odaa joaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi makaami inikaЙЎМ¶awepodi. Jemaatiwaji mida ЙЎМ¶adixakedi mawii anele, idiЙЎМ¶ida ajemaa doЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji mawii ane beyagi.
\v 20 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji joaniЙЎМ¶iniaaЙЎМ¶eote mele ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena. Aleegi, odaa eote manigaanyetece ЙЎМ¶odaxakawa SatanГЎs. Jemaa ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus Cristo midioka limedi meletedaЙЎМ¶adomitiwaji. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee. (AmГ©m).
\p 
\v 21 TimГіteo ane ibakawa yecoaditibigaЙЎМ¶ajitiwaji. LГәcio, JasГЈo, iniaa SosГӯpatro anida aneetege yoiigi, aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a oyecoaditibigaЙЎМ¶ajitiwaji.
\v 22 Eemoda Tertius ane jidi niЙЎМ¶inoa Paulo lotaЙЎМ¶a, aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a idecoaditibigaЙЎМ¶ajitiwaji, leeЙЎМ¶odi okotawece oko nepilidi ЗӨoniotagodi.
\v 23 Ee Paulo yotokaЙЎМ¶adi liЙЎМ¶eladi Gaio, odaa ele me dibatigi. Codaa niЙЎМ¶ina loiigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji digoina idioka limedi me latecaЙЎМ¶adi liЙЎМ¶eladi Gaio. Gaio aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yecoaditibigaЙЎМ¶ajitiwaji. Erasto, niЙЎМ¶ina ane doweditelogo ninyeelo nigotaЙЎМ¶a, iniaa ЙЎМ¶onioxoa Quarto eledi oyecoaditibigaЙЎМ¶ajitiwaji.
\v 24 Jemaa ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus Cristo midioka limedi meletedaЙЎМ¶adomitiwaji. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee. (AmГ©m).
\s1 Paulo doЙЎМ¶etetibigimece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji
\p 
\v 25 JoЙЎМ¶eeЙЎМ¶atalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Yakadi mepaanaЙЎМ¶a yoniciwaЙЎМ¶adi ЙЎМ¶atiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi. JiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eeta niЙЎМ¶inoa nibodicetedi anele anejitece, niЙЎМ¶ina me jiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece Jesus Cristo. NiЙЎМ¶inoa ane jiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶atece akaaЙЎМ¶inoa niЙЎМ¶ica maleekoka dinoe niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o. Pida jotigide aЙЎМ¶ica ane yowooЙЎМ¶odi. Natigide AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja nikeetedoЙЎМ¶owa.
\v 26 NiЙЎМ¶ijo ane daЙЎМ¶a jowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a ane diitigi midiwataЙЎМ¶a lotaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, anoyalaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane daЙЎМ¶a jowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja ikee. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji anidioka limedi me yewiЙЎМ¶a, niwakatee niЙЎМ¶idi oko moyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lotaЙЎМ¶a. Eote minatawece ane noiigi owajipatalo lotaЙЎМ¶a, eotedibige minatawece oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi, codaa monakato ЗӨoniotagodi.
\p 
\v 27 Iniokiniwateda me ЗӨonoenoЙЎМ¶odi, codaa iniokiniwateda minoa lixaketedi. Odaa leeditibige midioka limedi me joЙЎМ¶eeЙЎМ¶atalo leeЙЎМ¶odi ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus Cristo. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee. (AmГ©m).
